(115, 'Amarnath Package with Helicopter Service', 'amarnath-package-with-helicopter-service', '<p>An annual pilgrimage of spiritual significance, the Amarnath Yatra draws thousands of devotees. The difficult journey to the revered Amarnath Cave can be physically taxing for many, particularly for pilgrims who are elderly or have health issues. Helicopter services for the Amarnath Yatra are revolutionary in this regard.</p>\r\n<p><strong>What Are Amarnath Yatra Helicopter Services?</strong><br>From important places like Jammu, Srinagar, or Pahalgam, helicopter services offer air transportation to the base camps or closer to the Amarnath Cave. With this option, a greater number of devotees can participate in the pilgrimage because it significantly cuts down on travel time and physical strain.</p>\r\n<p>Advantages of Selecting Helicopter Services:<br>Time-saving: A helicopter can complete a task that would take days on foot in a matter of minutes.</p>\r\n<p>Comfort and Security: Steer clear of the physically.</p>', '1747998406.jpg', 'draft', NULL, '2025-05-23 11:06:46', '2025-05-23 11:06:46'),
