(21, 'Prilgimage Packages', 'Short Ammarnath Package', 'admin@joy.com', '1', '1715765111.jpg', '<p>A poet once exclaimed about Kashmir, &ldquo;If there is Heaven on Earth, it is here!&rdquo;And almost all visitors to this destination would vouch for this. Popularly known as the Switzerland of India, Kashmir is one of the most picturesque places in the world.</p>', '4', '3', 'Srinagar,Amarnath,Baltal,Sonmarg', 'Srinagar International Airport', 'Srinagar International Airport', '14999', '', 'Best Discounted Offer', '9600', '9906786356', '2024-05-15 09:25:11', '2025-05-24 06:45:16', '1N Srinagar', '.1N Sonmarg', '1N Houseboat', 'Accommodation at hotel\r\nWelcome drink on arrival\r\nDaily breakfast and dinner\r\nNon A/C Vehicle for sightseeing\r\nAirport/Train Station Transfer\r\nAll applicable taxes', '5 % GST\r\nEntry fees to monuments and Palaces\r\nAny meals not mentioned, Any transfers, Any insurance\r\nAnything not mentioned in the inclusions', 'Travel Validity\r\nThe date is valid for travel till Tuesday, 30 September 2025.\r\n\r\nEasy Cancellation Policy\r\nIn case of more than 30 days prior to departure date, initial booking amount and any additional amount of air fare will be charged as penalty. *Less than 30 days: 50% of total tour cost will be charged as penalty.\r\n\r\nGuaranteed Dates\r\nYour selected travel dates are guaranteed in the unlikely event of a death and not due guarantee * - 12 days from your preferred dates.', NULL),
(22, 'Prilgimage Packages', 'Kashmir with Vaishno Devi Darshan', 'admin@joy.com', '1', '1715765470.jpg', '<p>Jammu City is also known as \"City of Temples\" as it has many temples and shrines, with glittering shikhars soaring into the sky, which dot the citys skyline, creating the ambiance of a holy and peaceful Hindu city.Katra (50 kms from Jammu) is visited for Vaishnodevi temple and the town is base camp for visiting the famous Ma Vaishnodevi Shrine (5,300 ft asl), which is 13 Km uphill walk from Katra.The Mata Vaishno Devi Shrine is linked to the Base Camp Katra with a 13 Kms track. The entire uphill Journey from Katra to Bhawan is on foot, however, one can hire ponies, palkies or pithoo for ease of journey. Pahalgam, located in the high Himalayas in the Lidder valley. Travel to Pahalgam is an ideal destination for hiking, trekking and fishing.Gulmarg literally means the meadow of flowers.It attracts various tourists due to its natural beauty. The snow-clad peaks and the lovely landscapes.The capital of Jammu and Kashmir and the largest city in the state, Srinagar (1,730m) is famous for its canals, houseboats and Mughal gardens.One of the unique charm of Srinagar are the houseboats. The houseboats are the floating little hotels which can be seen on the edge of the Dal Lake or in the secluded areas of the Nagin Lake.</p>', '11', '10', 'Srinagar,Gulmarg,Pahalgam,Sonmarg', 'Srinagar International Airport', 'Jammu Airport', '18999', '', 'Most Selling Package', '13999', '9906786356', '2024-05-15 09:31:10', '2025-05-24 06:48:50', '5N Srinagar | 1N Gulmarg', '1N Pahalgam | 1N Sonmarg', '1N Patnitop | 1N Katra', 'Accommodation at hotel\r\nWelcome drink on arrival\r\nDaily breakfast and dinner\r\nNon A/C Vehicle for sightseeing\r\nAirport/Train Station Transfer\r\nAll applicable taxes', '5 % GST\r\nEntry fees to monuments and Palaces\r\nAny meals not mentioned, Any transfers, Any insurance\r\nAnything not mentioned in the inclusions', 'Travel Validity\r\nThe date is vali