(28, 'Ladakh Tour Packages', 'Joy Ladakh Expedition', 'admin@joy.com', '1', '1724917168.jpg', '<p>Embark on a thrilling journey through Ladakh\'s wild terrain, towering peaks, breathtaking views, and boundless adventures, creating unforgettable memories at every turn. &gt; Experience the intriguing phenomenon of Magnetic Hills, where vehicles seem to defy gravity, offering an unforgettable roadside marvel in Ladakh. &gt; At Sangam Point, witness the mesmerizing convergence of the Zanskar and Indus rivers, a breathtaking natural sight that adds to the beauty of Ladakh landscapes. &gt; Embark on an unforgettable adventure through Nubra Valley atop a Bactrian camel, immersing yourself in the tranquil beauty of the cold desert &gt; Marvel at the color changing beauty of Pangong Tso, where the crystal-clear waters mirror the majestic Himalayas.</p>', '6', '5', 'Leh Local,Nubra Valley,Pangong Lake,Sham Valley', 'Kushok Bakula Rimpochee Airport', 'Kushok Bakula Rimpochee Airport', '34000', '', 'Promotional Offer', '24999', '9906786356', '2024-08-29 07:39:28', '2025-05-20 09:50:18', '3N Leh', '1N Nubra', '1N Pangong', 'Accommodation at hotel\r\nWelcome drink on arrival\r\nDaily breakfast and dinner\r\nNon A/C Vehicle for sightseeing\r\nAirport/Train Station Transfer\r\nAll applicable taxes', '5 % GST\r\nEntry fees to monuments and Palaces\r\nAny meals not mentioned, Any transfers, Any insurance\r\nAnything not mentioned in the inclusions', 'Travel Validity\r\nThe date is valid for travel till Tuesday, 30 September 2025.\r\n\r\nEasy Cancellation Policy\r\nIn case of more than 30 days prior to departure date, initial booking amount and any additional amount of air fare will be charged as penalty. *Less than 30 days: 50% of total tour cost will be charged as penalty.\r\n\r\nGuaranteed Dates\r\nYour selected travel dates are guaranteed in the unlikely event of a death and not due guarantee * - 12 days from your preferred dates.', NULL),
(29, 'Ladakh Tour Packages', 'Joy Ladakh Adventure', 'admin@joy.com', '1', '1724917735.jpg', '<p>&gt; Begin an incredible adventure as you explore the rough terrain and diverse culture of Ladakh, where the land is rugged and the traditions are rich. &gt; Leh through a sightseeing tour, immersing yourself in the vibrant atmosphere of Leh Market, marveling at the historical Leh Palace, and finding serenity at the iconic Shanti Stupa. &gt; Embark on an exciting trip to Sham Valley, where you\'ll experience the wonders of Magnetic Hill, Gurudwara Pathar Sahib, and a visit to SECMOL, the school featured in the real-life 3-idiots movie. &gt; the breathtaking views of Nubra Valley and the exciting journey along the winding roads of the all season motorable Khardung-La Pass.</p>', '7', '6', 'Leh local,Nubra Valley,Pangong Lake,Sham Valley', 'Kushok Bakula Rimpochee Airport', 'Kushok Bakula Rimpochee Airport', '29999', '', 'Early Season Sale', '31000', '9906786356', '2024-08-29 07:48:55', '2025-05-22 09:33:38', '4N Leh', '1N Nubra', '1N Pangong', 'Accommodation at hotel\r\nWelcome drink on arrival\r\nDaily breakfast and dinner\r\nNon A/C Vehicle for sightseeing\r\nAirport/Train Station Transfer\r\nAll applicable taxes', '5 % GST\r\nEntry fees to monuments and Palaces\r\nAny meals not mentioned, Any transfers, Any insurance\r\nAnything not mentioned in the inclusions', 'Travel Validity\r\nThe date is valid for travel till Tuesday, 30 September 2025.\r\n\r\nEasy Cancellation Policy\r\nIn case of more than 30 days prior to departure date, initial booking amount and any additional amount of air fare will be charged as penalty. *Less than 30 days: 50% of total tour cost will be charged as penalty.\r\n\r\nGuaranteed Dates\r\nYour selected travel dates are guaranteed in the unlikely event of a death and not due guarantee * - 12 days from your preferred dates.', NULL),
