(32, 'Ladakh Tour Packages', 'Kashmir Ladakh Manali Tour Package', 'admin@joy.com', '1', '1725425659.jpg', '<p>&gt; Drass village, the second coldest inhabited place in the world, is one of the most scenic locations of the country along with its strategic significance. Pay your tributes to the Indian soldiers who laid down their lives during the Kargil war at the War Memorial of the region &gt; Explore the spectacular Pangong Lake, the world\'s highest saltwater lake, nestled amidst majestic snow-capped mountains, and take a leisurely stroll along its picturesque shoreline &gt; Uncover the wonders of modern engineering at the Atal Tunnel, world\'s longest underground tunnels, 10,000 feet above the ground that stretches over 9 kilometres &gt; Experience the excitement of camel rides amidst the captivating sand dunes of Nubra Valley &gt; Embark on an adventurous journey through the renowned Gata Loops, a series of 21 hairpin bends that wind their way to the summit of NakeeLa Pass, which is widely considered as one of the most elevated motorable routes in the Ladakh region</p>', '11', '10', 'Kargil,Nubra,Pangong,Hanle', 'Srinagar International Airport', 'Kushok Bakula Rimpochee Airport', '36900', '', 'Fuel Your Soul with Travel', '39999', '9906786356', '2024-08-29 08:24:23', '2025-05-22 11:02:26', '3N Leh', '1N Kargil', '1N Pangong', 'Accommodation at hotel\r\nWelcome drink on arrival\r\nDaily breakfast and dinner\r\nNon A/C Vehicle for sightseeing\r\nAirport/Train Station Transfer\r\nAll applicable taxes', '5 % GST\r\nEntry fees to monuments and Palaces\r\nAny meals not mentioned, Any transfers, Any insurance\r\nAnything not mentioned in the inclusions', 'Travel Validity\r\nThe date is valid for travel till Tuesday, 30 September 2025.\r\n\r\nEasy Cancellation Policy\r\nIn case of more than 30 days prior to departure date, initial booking amount and any additional amount of air fare will be charged as penalty. *Less than 30 days: 50% of total tour cost will be charged 