(33, 'Kashmir Tour Packages', 'Kashmir With Off-Beat Places', 'admin@joy.com', '1', '1726651773.jpg', '<p>Spend a Beautiful vacation in Kashmir with Kashmir\'s Off-Beat Places Like Aharbal Waterfall, Daksum, Bangus Valley. Daksum is a natural scenic spot located in the Larnoo tehsil of Anantnag district, Jammu and Kashmir, at Anantnag-Semthan-Kishtwar road (NH-244). Any visitor to Bangus will undoubtedly be taken aback by its enduring allure. The majority of activities in the Valley include discovering it on one&rsquo;s own and absorbing the aura of its beauty. Permits were once required from the District Magistrate in Kupwara for a hike in the Valley. The Valley has recently experienced an increase in tourism and is gradually making its way into the quirky areas frequently visited by visitors in the region. Visitors can sleep at the Bangus Camping site for an exciting experience and see the Valley itself.</p>', '9', '8', 'Doodhpathri,Yusmarg,Pahalgam,Gulmarg', 'Srinagar International Airport', 'Srinagar International Airport', '11999', '', 'Happiness on Earth', '10999', '9906786356', '2024-09-18 09:29:33', '2025-05-22 10:38:15', '4N Srinagar', '1N Gulmarg Valley | 1N Pahalgam', '1N Sonmarg', 'Accommodation at hotel\r\nWelcome drink on arrival\r\nDaily breakfast and dinner\r\nNon A/C Vehicle for sightseeing\r\nAirport/Train Station Transfer\r\nAll applicable taxes', '5 % GST\r\nEntry fees to monuments and Palaces\r\nAny meals not mentioned, Any transfers, Any insurance\r\nAnything not mentioned in the inclusions', 'Travel Validity\r\nThe date is valid for travel till Tuesday, 30 September 2025.\r\n\r\nEasy Cancellation Policy\r\nIn case of more than 30 days prior to departure date, initial booking amount and any additional amount of air fare will be charged as penalty. *Less than 30 days: 50% of total tour cost will be charged as penalty.\r\n\r\nGuaranteed Dates\r\nYour selected travel dates are guaranteed in the unlikely event of a death and not due guarantee * - 1