(39, 'Ladakh Tour Packages', 'Exclusive Manali Leh Srinagar', 'admin@joy.com', '1', '1726733479.jpg', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><strong>Exclusive Manali Leh Srinagar | Free Shikara Ride Highlights A perfect blend of adventurous, thrilling and cultural experiences, handpicked by Joy Travels outdoor experts Visit pangong lake; world&rsquo;s highest saltwater lake that changes its colour from shades of blue to green to red Let the adrenaline rush pump through your veins as you drive through the world&rsquo;s highest motorable passes like Khardung la and lachung la, rohtang la, and Baralacha la. Explore the \'Heaven on Earth - Srinagar\' with a famous Shikara ride along with a chance to sojourn in a unique houseboat Experience Himalayan region with utmost safety and comfort in well sanitized accommodation and vehicles</strong></span></p>', '11', '10', 'Nubra via Khardung La Pass,Srinagar.,Manali,Sarchu', 'Manali Halt Railway Station or Bus Stand', 'Srinagar International Airport', '71000', '', 'Free Shikara Ride', '64999', '9906786356', '2024-09-19 08:11:19', '2025-05-29 07:32:11', '1N Manali | 1N Jispa | 1N Sarchu', '3N Leh | 1N Nubra | 1N Pangong', '1N Kargil | 1N Srinagar', 'Accommodation at hotel\r\nWelcome drink on arrival\r\nDaily breakfast and dinner\r\nNon A/C Vehicle for sightseeing\r\nAirport/Train Station Transfer\r\nAll applicable taxes', '5 % GST\r\nEntry fees to monuments and Palaces\r\nAny meals not mentioned, Any transfers, Any insurance\r\nAnything not mentioned in the inclusions', 'Travel Validity\r\nThe date is valid for travel till Tuesday, 30 September 2025.\r\n\r\nEasy Cancellation Policy\r\nIn case of more than 30 days prior to departure date, initial booking amount and any additional amount of air fare will be charged as penalty. *Less than 30 days: 50% of total tour cost will be charged as penalty.\r\n\r\nGuaranteed Dates\r\nYour selected travel dates are guaranteed in the unlikely event of a death and not due guarantee * - 12 day