(50, 'Prilgimage Packages', 'Amarnath Yatra Helicopter Tour Package', 'admin@joy.com', '1', '1727076617.jpg', '<p>Marvel at the naturally formed Shiva lingam, a sacred ice stalagmite that attracts thousands of pilgrims seeking blessings and spiritual solace. Explore the natural wonder of Amarnath Cave by helicopter ride and bask in the beauty of Sonmarg\'s lush meadows. Embark on a scenic journey to Sonmarg on a horseback ride and witness the majestic Thajiwas Glacier. Soar above the beautiful Himalayas on a 15-minute helicopter ride from Neelgrath to Panjtarni helipads and enjoy convenient access to Shri Amarnath Cave Temple. Pay homage to the holy Amarnath Shrine and seek blessings from Lord Shiva in the naturally formed Shiva lingam.</p>', '3', '2', 'Srinagar,Amarnath shrine,Baltal,Sonmarg', 'Srinagar International Airport', 'Srinagar International Airport', '20000', '', 'Keep Calm and Travel On', '15500', '9906786356', '2024-09-23 07:30:17', '2025-05-24 07:19:09', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Accommodation at hotel\r\nWelcome drink on arrival\r\nDaily breakfast and dinner\r\nNon A/C Vehicle for sightseeing\r\nAirport/Train Station Transfer\r\nAll applicable taxes', '5 % GST\r\nEntry fees to monuments and Palaces\r\nAny meals not mentioned, Any transfers, Any insurance\r\nAnything not mentioned in the inclusions', 'Travel Validity\r\nThe date is valid for travel till Tuesday, 30 September 2025.\r\n\r\nEasy Cancellation Policy\r\nIn case of more than 30 days prior to departure date, initial booking amount and any additional amount of air fare will be charged as penalty. *Less than 30 days: 50% of total tour cost will be charged as penalty.\r\n\r\nGuaranteed Dates\r\nYour selected travel dates are guaranteed in the unlikely event of a death and not due guarantee * - 12 days from your preferred dates.', NULL),
(51, 'Kashmir Tour Packages', 'Kashmir Holidays | Houseboat Experience and Beyond', 'admin@joy.com', '1', '1727163539.jpg', '<p>Explore Srinagar\'s Dal Lake and witness iconic attractions in Sonmarg, Pahalgam and Gulmarg on this adventurous trip to Kashmir. From scenic valleys like Aru and Betaab to Himalayan views and glaciers of Chandanwari, discover the diverse beauty of Pahalgam. Embark on a peaceful shikara ride on Dal Lake and see the vibrant blooms of Badamwari Garden in Srinagar. Channel your inner explorer with a horseback ride through Sonmarg\'s meadows and marvel at the gigantic Thajiwas Glacier. Witness breathtaking views from Gulmarg\'s Gondola, followed by a visit to the Drung Waterfall, a hidden gem nestled amidst the mountains.</p>', '6', '5', 'Srinagar,Pahalgam,Gulmarg,Sonmarg', 'Srinagar International Airport', 'Srinagar International Airport', '38333', '', 'From Snow to Serenity', '21850', '9906786356', '2024-09-24 07:38:59', '2025-05-24 07:26:10', '3N Srinagar', '1N Pahalgam', '1N Houseboat', 'Accommodation at hotel\r\nWelcome drink on arrival\r\nDaily breakfast and dinner\r\nNon A/C Vehicle for sightseeing\r\nAirport/Train Station Transfer\r\nAll applicable taxes', '5 % GST\r\nEntry fees to monuments and Palaces\r\nAny meals not mentioned, Any transfers, Any insurance\r\nAnything not mentioned in the inclusions', 'Travel Validity\r\nThe date is valid for travel till Tuesday, 30 September 2025.\r\n\r\nEasy Cancellation Policy\r\nIn case of more than 30 days prior to departure date, initial booking amount and any additional amount of air fare will be charged as penalty. *Less than 30 days: 50% of total tour cost will be charged as penalty.\r\n\r\nGuaranteed Dates\r\nYour selected travel dates are guaranteed in the unlikely event of a death and not due guarantee * - 12 days from your preferred dates.', NULL),
(52, 'Kashmir Tour Packages', 'Splendors of Kashmir | An Unforgettable Experience', 'admin@joy.com', '1', '1741159076.jpg', '<p>From snow-capped peaks and stunning lakes to lush meadows and wonderful attractions, enjoy a vacation in Kashmir, the Paradise on Earth. Immerse yourself in the beauty of the Himalayas as you board the Shikara on Dal Lake, the second-largest lake in Jammu and Kashmir. Explore the famous Betaab Valley, named after the iconic Bollywood movie \'Betaab,\' and take-in the panoramic views of the surroundings. Enjoy the world\'s second-highest operating cable car, the Gulmarg Gondola, and admire the views of the Himalayan peaks and alpine meadows.</p>', '8', '7', 'Gulmarg,Sonmarg,Doodhpathri,Pahalgam', 'Srinagar International Airport', 'Srinagar International Airport', '41850', '', 'Fly The Friendly Skies', '24999', '9906786356', '2024-09-24 07:46:06', '2025-05-24 07:35:33', '4N Srinagar', '2N Pahalgam', '1N Houseboat', 'Accommodation at hotel\r\nWelcome drink on arrival\r\nDaily breakfast and dinner\r\nNon A/C Vehicle for sightseeing\r\nAirport/Train Station Transfer\r\nAll applicable taxes', '5 % GST\r\nEntry fees to monuments and Palaces\r\nAny meals not mentioned, Any transfers, Any insurance\r\nAnything not mentioned in the inclusions', 'Travel Validity\r\nThe date is valid for travel till Tuesday, 30 September 2025.\r\n\r\nEasy Cancellation Policy\r\nIn case of more than 30 days prior to departure date, initial booking amount and any additional amount of air fare will be charged as penalty. *Less than 30 days: 50% of total tour cost will be charged as penalty.\r\n\r\nGuaranteed Dates\r\nYour selected travel dates are guaranteed in the unlikely event of a death and not due guarantee * - 12 days from your preferred dates.', NULL);
