(62, 'Ladakh Tour Packages', 'Ladakh Unveiled: From Peaks to Dunes', 'admin@joy.com', '1', '1745489766.jpg', '<p class=\"\" data-start=\"152\" data-end=\"527\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"152\" data-end=\"527\">Embark on a soul-stirring journey through the mystical landscapes of Ladakh &mdash; where snow-capped peaks kiss the sky and golden dunes whisper stories of ancient caravans. This immersive package blends high-altitude adventure with serene desert charm, guiding you from the iconic monasteries and azure lakes of Leh to the surreal beauty of the Hunder Sand Dunes in Nubra Valley.</p>\r\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"529\" data-end=\"552\"><strong data-start=\"529\" data-end=\"552\">Highlights include:</strong></p>\r\n<ul data-start=\"553\" data-end=\"869\">\r\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"553\" data-end=\"604\">\r\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"555\" data-end=\"604\">Exploring the vibrant culture and heritage of Leh</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"605\" data-end=\"670\">\r\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"607\" data-end=\"670\">Witnessing the tranquility of Pangong Lake&rsquo;s ever-changing hues</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"671\" data-end=\"722\">\r\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"673\" data-end=\"722\">Driving through the world-famous Khardung La Pass</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"723\" data-end=\"799\">\r\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"725\" data-end=\"799\">Experiencing a camel safari on the double-humped Bactrian camels in Hunder</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"800\" data-end=\"869\">\r\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"802\" data-end=\"869\">Visiting ancient monasteries nestled in dramatic mountain backdrops</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>', '8', '7', 'Leh,Nubra,Khardunglapas,Pangong,Lake,ChanglaPas,Kargil', 'Leh Airport', 'Srinagar Airport', '45000', NULL, 'Journey to the Roof of the World', '38000', '9906786356', '2025-04-24 10:16:06', '2025-04-24 10:16:06', '3N Leh', '1N Nubra', '1N Pangong', 'Accommodation at hotel\r\nW