(69, 'Ladakh Tour Packages', 'High Roads & Himalayan Dreams', 'admin@joy.com', '1', '1745565379.jpg', '<p class=\"\" data-start=\"234\" data-end=\"613\">Embark on a breathtaking journey through the heart of the Indian Himalayas, blending the enchanting charm of <strong data-start=\"343\" data-end=\"353\">Manali</strong> with the rugged beauty and awe-inspiring landscapes of <strong data-start=\"409\" data-end=\"419\">Ladakh</strong>. This 5 Nights / 6 Days itinerary is perfect for adventure seekers, nature lovers, and anyone ready to experience the unmatched beauty of two of the most famous Himalayan destinations in India.</p>\r\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"615\" data-end=\"1066\">From Manali&rsquo;s lush greenery and snow-capped peaks to the barren yet stunningly beautiful landscapes of Ladakh, this trip will take you through high mountain passes, picturesque villages, and majestic monasteries, all while riding along some of the world&rsquo;s most challenging roads. Whether it&rsquo;s the serenity of <strong data-start=\"924\" data-end=\"940\">Pangong Lake</strong>, the adventure of <strong data-start=\"959\" data-end=\"974\">Khardung La</strong>, or the cultural richness of Leh, this journey is designed to be a soul-stirring adventure.</p>', '06', '05', 'Day 1: Arrival in Manali ‚Äì Local Sightseeing,Day 2: Manali ‚Äì Atal Tunnel ‚Äì Sissu ‚Äì Jispa,Day 3: Jispa to Leh via Baralacha Pass,Day 4: Leh Local Sightseeing,Day 5: Day Trip to Khardung La / Pangong Lake Option,Day 6: Departure from Leh', 'Delhi Airport', 'Leh Airport', '35000', NULL, 'From Snow to Serenity ‚Äì Live the Magic in 6 Days', '29000', '9906786356', '2025-04-25 07:16:19', '2025-04-25 07:16:19', 'Manali / Atal tunnel / Sissu / Jispa', 'Leh / Baralacha Pass', 'Leh / Khardung La / Pangong Lake', 'Accommodation at hotel\r\nWelcome drink on arrival\r\nDaily breakfast and dinner\r\nNon A/C Vehicle for sightseeing\r\nAirport/Train Station Transfer\r\nAll applicable taxes', '5 % GST\r\nEntry fees to monum