(73, 'Kashmir Tour Packages', '6 Nights / 7 Days Ladakh Adventure Tour', 'admin@joy.com', '1', '1748679028.jpg', '<p class=\"\" data-start=\"176\" data-end=\"714\">Ladakh, often referred to as &ldquo;The Land of High Passes,&rdquo; is a region of stark beauty, characterized by towering snow-capped mountains, vast barren landscapes, and shimmering high-altitude lakes. This <strong data-start=\"375\" data-end=\"408\">6 Nights / 7 Days Ladakh tour</strong> takes you on an unforgettable adventure through the pristine beauty of Ladakh&rsquo;s most iconic destinations, including <strong data-start=\"525\" data-end=\"532\">Leh</strong>, <strong data-start=\"534\" data-end=\"550\">Nubra Valley</strong>, <strong data-start=\"552\" data-end=\"568\">Pangong Lake</strong>, and <strong data-start=\"574\" data-end=\"588\">Tso Moriri</strong>. Along the way, you&rsquo;ll experience a blend of cultural richness, stunning natural wonders, and thrilling high-altitude drives.</p>\r\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"716\" data-end=\"923\">Perfect for adventure seekers, nature lovers, and photography enthusiasts, this itinerary is designed to offer a balance between exploring Ladakh&rsquo;s cultural heritage and enjoying its unparalleled landscapes.</p>', '07', '06', 'Leh,Nubra,Pangong,Tso Moriri', 'Kushok Bakula Rimpochee ( Leh Airport)', 'Kushok Bakula Rimpochee ( Leh Airport)', '29000', NULL, '7 Days of Majestic Landscapes and Ancient Culture', '23000', '9906786356', '2025-04-25 07:24:59', '2025-05-31 08:10:28', '2N Leh', '1N Nubra', '1N Pangong | 1N Tso Moriri', 'Accommodation at hotel\r\nWelcome drink on arrival\r\nDaily breakfast and dinner\r\nNon A/C Vehicle for sightseeing\r\nAirport/Train Station Transfer\r\nAll applicable taxes', '5 % GST\r\nEntry fees to monuments and Palaces\r\nAny meals not mentioned, Any transfers, Any insurance\r\nAnything not mentioned in the inclusions', 'Travel Validity\r\nThe date is valid for travel till Tuesday, 30 September 2025.\r\n\r\nEasy Cancellation