(80, 'Ladakh Tour Packages', 'Joy Magical Ladakh', 'admin@joy.com', '1', '1745577774.jpg', '<p class=\"dest-guide-header\">Your Ladakh Destination Guide</p>\r\n<p>Witness the breathtaking wonders of Leh on this holiday! Explore Leh Palace, unwind by the pristine Pangong Lake, visit the Sangam and cross the Khardung La Pass. With inner line permits and environment fee sorted for you, enjoy hassle-free travel.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '6', '5', 'Day : 1 Leh  Meet and greet on arrival at Kushok Bakula Rimpochee - Leh airport and transfer to the hotel. Full day free for acclimatization. You are advised to stay and relax in the hotel. It‚Äôs important to take rest for 24 hours and wear heavy woolens. O/N Leh.,Day : 2 Leh City Sightseeing After breakfast proceed for Leh city sightseeing which includes Hemis Monastery Oldest and richest monastery of Ladakh Thiksey Monastery Historic Buddhist monastery on a Hill Shey palace and Sindhu Ghat Rancho School subject to permission Hall of fame museum ‚Äì Indian army operated memorial & museum Shanti stupa Domed Buddhist temple on a hill and Leh Palace Centuries old mountaintop palace. Evening explore Leh market. O/N Leh.,Day : 3 Leh ‚Äì Nubra Valley After early breakfast leave for Nubra valley (5-6 hrs drive) via Khardungla pass @ 18380 ft (World‚Äôs highest motor-able road). Reach Nubra valley by afternoon. Nubra Valley offers tremendous scenery on a grand scale with green oasis villages surrounded by thrillingly stark scree slopes and harsh arid mountains. You can enjoy Two hump camel safari on the World‚Äôs highest coldest desert at own expenses. O/N Nubra Valley.,Day : 4 Nubra Valley ‚Äì Leh After breakfast proceed for Leh by same route via Diskit ‚Äì Future Buddha Statue & Khardungla pass. O/N Leh,Day : 5 Leh ‚Äì Pangong Lake ‚Äì Leh (8-9 hrs drive both ways) After early breakfast leave for Pangong Lake through Changla pass (17350 ft - world‚Äôs third highest motorable road). Pangong Lake is at an altitude of 14500 ft and is World‚Äôs highest and longest salt water lake. Enjoy changing colours of the Blue brackish Lake. Back to leh by evening. O/N Leh.,Day : 6 Final Departure Today morning drop at Leh airport to catch flight for onward journey. The tour ends here with the sweet memories of Joy Tours.', 'Leh Airport', 'Leh Airport', '37000', NULL, 'Enjoy Camel Safari', '29000', '9906786356', '2025-04-25 10:42:54', '2025-04-25 10:42:54', '3N Leh', '1N Nubra', '1N Pangong', 'Accommodation at hotel\r\nWelcome drink on arrival\r\nDaily breakfast and dinner\r\nNon A/C Vehicle for sightseeing\r\nAirport/Train Station Transfer\r\nAll applicable taxes', '5 % GST\r\nEntry fees to monuments and Palaces\r\nAny meals not mentioned, Any transfers, Any insurance\r\nAnything not mentioned in the inclusions', 'Travel Validity\r\nThe date is valid for travel till Tuesday, 30 September 2025.\r\n\r\nEasy Cancellation Policy\r\nIn case of more than 30 days prior to departure date, initial booking amount and any additional amount of air fare will be charged as penalty. *Less than 30 days: 50% of total tour cost will be charged as penalty.\r\n\r\nGuaranteed Dates\r\nYour selected travel dates are guaranteed in the unlikely event of a death and not due guarantee * - 12 days from your preferred dates.', NULL),
(81, 'Kashmir Tour Packages', 'JOY EXOTIC KASHMIR', 'admin@joy.com', '1', '1745580006.jpg', '<p><strong><span data-huuid=\"8618053696195318476\">Kashmir offer a mix of natural beauty and historical significance. </span><span data-huuid=\"8618053696195319319\">Kashmir, particularly around Srinagar, is known for its scenic Chinar trees, Dal Lake, and Shikara rides.&nbsp;</span></strong></p>', '6', '5', 'DalLake,Gulmarg,Pahalgam', 'Srinagar International Airport', 'Srinagar International Airport', '31000', NULL, 'Trending Package', '18000', '9906786356', '2025-04-25 11:20:06', '2025-05-27 08:02:42', '2N Srinagar', '2N Pahalgam', '1N Gulmarg', 'Welcome assistance on Arrival.\r\nAccommodation in mentioned or similar hotels as per the itinerary (In base category room).\r\nAll transfers and sightseeing (Private/Independent) as per itinerary by Non AC Vehicle.\r\nAll currently applicable hotel taxes except Govt Service Tax as per prevailing rates.\r\nMeal Plan - As Per The Package.\r\nChild below 05 Years Complimentary.', 'Any expenses of personal nature like ‚Äì tips, portages, mineral water, telephone calls, laundry, Gst etc.\r\nStill / video camera fees during the tour\r\nAny flight / train ticket fare\r\nGuide service at any place\r\nSightseeing at Pahalgam (Chandanwari & Aru Valley), Sonmarg (Zero Point), Gulmarg (Chain\r\nVehcle or Drung Water Fall) or any local vehicle wherever our vehicle will not be permitted by local\r\nunion or Govt instructions.\r\nAny other item / services which is not mentioned in the above head Inclusions.\r\nAccidental cost due to bad weather or due to any restriction in the area, flight cancellations etc.\r\nCost incidental to any change in the itinerary / stay on account of flight cancellation, ill health,\r\nroadblocks and /Natural Calamities.\r\nExpenses caused by factors beyond our control like rail and flight delays, roadblocks, vehicle malfunctions, political disturbances etc\r\nEntrance fees at the monuments.\r\nMeals other than men