(84, 'Kashmir Tour Packages', 'JOY KASHMIR WITH KHYBER', 'admin@joy.com', '1', '1745647990.jpg', '<p data-start=\"87\" data-end=\"150\"><strong data-start=\"87\" data-end=\"150\">Gulmarg Valley: A Scenic and Adventurous Retreat in Kashmir</strong></p>\r\n<p data-start=\"152\" data-end=\"302\"><span class=\"relative -mx-px my-[-0.2rem] rounded px-px py-[0.2rem] transition-colors duration-100 ease-in-out\">Nestled in the Pir Panjal Range of Jammu &amp; Kashmir, <strong data-start=\"52\" data-end=\"63\">Gulmarg</strong> is a picturesque hill station renowned for its lush meadows, snow-capped peaks, and vibrant flora.</span> <span class=\"relative -mx-px my-[-0.2rem] rounded px-px py-[0.2rem] transition-colors duration-100 ease-in-out\">Approximately 60 kilometers from Srinagar, it is accessible via a scenic drive through dense pine forests and rolling hills.</span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"304\" data-end=\"335\"><strong data-start=\"304\" data-end=\"335\">Top Attractions in Gulmarg:</strong></p>\r\n<ul data-start=\"337\" data-end=\"1445\">\r\n<li data-start=\"337\" data-end=\"518\">\r\n<p data-start=\"339\" data-end=\"518\"><strong data-start=\"339\" data-end=\"359\">Gulmarg Gondola:</strong> <span class=\"relative -mx-px my-[-0.2rem] rounded px-px py-[0.2rem] transition-colors duration-100 ease-in-out\">As one of the world\'s highest cable cars, the Gulmarg Gondola offers breathtaking views as it ascends to Kongdori (3,080 meters) and Apharwat Peak (3,950 meters).</span> <span class=\"relative -mx-px my-[-0.2rem] rounded px-px py-[0.2rem] transition-colors duration-100 ease-in-out\">The two-stage gondola is a gateway to skiing and snowboarding adventures.</span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"520\" data-end=\"699\">\r\n<p data-start=\"522\" data-end=\"699\"><strong data-start=\"522\" data-end=\"540\">Apharwat Peak:</strong> <span class=\"relative -mx-px my-[-0.2rem] rounded px-px py-[0.2rem] transition-colors duration-100 ease-in-out\">Standing at 4,390 meters, Apharwat Peak is a haven for winter sports enthusiasts.</span> <span class=\"relative -mx-px my-[-0.2rem] rounded px-px py-[0.2rem] transition-colors duration-100 ease-in-out\">The surrounding slopes offer more than three acres of ski terrain, catering to both beginners and seasoned adventurers.</span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"701\" data-end=\"884\">\r\n<p data-start=\"703\" data-end=\"884\"><strong data-start=\"703\" data-end=\"725\">Strawberry Valley:</strong> <span class=\"relative -mx-px my-[-0.2rem] rounded px-px py-[0.2rem] transition-colors duration-100 ease-in-out\">During summer, this valley bursts into life with ripe strawberries.</span> <span class=\"relative -mx-px my-[-0.2rem] rounded px-px py-[0.2rem] transition-colors duration-100 ease-in-out\">Visitors can enjoy picnics amidst the greenery or embark on guided treks and horseback rides through its snowy paths in winter.</span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"886\" data-end=\"1077\">\r\n<p data-start=\"888\" data-end=\"1077\"><strong data-start=\"888\" data-end=\"918\">Gulmarg Biosphere Reserve:</strong> <span class=\"relative -mx-px my-[-0.2rem] rounded px-px py-[0.2rem] transition-colors duration-100 ease-in-out\">Spanning nearly 200 square kilometers, this reserve is home to diverse wildlife, including the rare musk deer, red foxes, and bears.</span> <span class=\"relative -mx-px my-[-0.2rem] rounded px-px py-[0.2rem] transition-colors duration-100 ease-in-out\">It\'s a paradise for nature enthusiasts and bird watchers.</span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"1079\" data-end=\"1260\">\r\n<p data-start=\"1081\" data-end=\"1260\"><strong data-start=\"1081\" data-end=\"1101\">Maharani Temple:</strong> <span class=\"relative -mx-px my-[-0.2rem] rounded px-px py-[0.2rem] transition-colors duration-100 ease-in-out\">Built in 1915 by Maharaja Hari Singh for his wife, Maharani Mohini Bai Sisodia, this temple is dedicated to Lord Shiva.</span> <span class=\"relative -mx-px my-[-0.2rem] rounded px-px py-[0.2rem] transition-colors duration-100 ease-in-out\">It offers panoramic views of the valley and is a symbol of the region\'s rich cultural heritage.</span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"1262\" data-end=\"1445\">\r\n<p data-start=\"1264\" data-end=\"1445\"><strong data-start=\"1264\" data-end=\"1286\">St. Mary\'s Church:</strong> <span class=\"relative -mx-px my-[-0.2rem] rounded px-px py-[0.2rem] transition-colors duration-100 ease-in-out\">Constructed in 1902 during British rule, this Victorian-style church is one of the oldest in the region.</span> <span class=\"relative -mx-px my-[-0.2rem] rounded px-px py-[0.2rem] transition-colors duration-100 ease-in-out\">Its serene ambiance and architectural beauty make it a must-visit for history and architecture enthusiasts.</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>', '5', '4', 'DalLake,Gulmarg,Srinagar,Sonmarg', 'Srinagar International Airport', 'Srinagar International Airport', '70000', NULL, 'Premium Package', '59999', '9906786356', '2025-04-26 06:13:10', '2025-05-31 06:40:09', '1N Srinagar', '1N Gulmarg', '2N Srinagar', 'Welcome assistance on Arrival.\r\nAccommodation in mentioned or similar hotels as per the itinerary (In base category room).\r\nAll transfers and sightseeing (Private/Independent) as per itinerary by Non AC Vehicle.\r\nAll currently applicable hotel taxes except Govt Service Tax as per prevailing rates.\r\nMeal Plan - As Per The Package.\r\nChild below 05 Years Complimentary.', 'Any expenses of personal nature like ‚Äì tips, portages, mineral water, telephone calls, laundry, Gst etc.\r\nStill / video camera fees during the tour\r\nAny flight / train ticket fare\r\nGuide service at any place\r\nSightseeing at Pahalgam (Chandanwari & Aru Valley), Sonmarg (Zero Point), Gulmarg (Chain\r\nVehcle or Drung Water Fall) or any local vehicle wherever our vehicle will not be permitted by local\r\nunion or Govt instructions.\r\nAny other item / services which is not mentioned in the above