(85, 'Kashmir Tour Packages', 'JOY EXOTIC KASHMIR WITH DAKSUM', 'admin@joy.com', '1', '1745648460.jpg', '<h3 data-start=\"346\" data-end=\"377\">Activities &amp; Attractions</h3>\r\n<ul data-start=\"379\" data-end=\"1103\">\r\n<li data-start=\"379\" data-end=\"563\">\r\n<p data-start=\"381\" data-end=\"563\"><strong data-start=\"381\" data-end=\"402\">Trekking &amp; Hiking</strong>: <span class=\"relative -mx-px my-[-0.2rem] rounded px-px py-[0.2rem] transition-colors duration-100 ease-in-out\">Daksum serves as a gateway for trekkers heading towards Sinthan Top and Sinthan Pass.</span> <span class=\"relative -mx-px my-[-0.2rem] rounded px-px py-[0.2rem] transition-colors duration-100 ease-in-out\">The trails, surrounded by alpine meadows and dense forests, offer both challenging and moderate treks, rewarding adventurers with panoramic views</span> .</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"565\" data-end=\"739\">\r\n<p data-start=\"567\" data-end=\"739\"><strong data-start=\"567\" data-end=\"578\">Camping</strong>: <span class=\"relative -mx-px my-[-0.2rem] rounded px-px py-[0.2rem] transition-colors duration-100 ease-in-out\">The valley\'s serene environment makes it an ideal spot for camping.</span> <span class=\"relative -mx-px my-[-0.2rem] rounded px-px py-[0.2rem] transition-colors duration-100 ease-in-out\">Visitors can pitch tents by the Brengi River, enjoying starlit skies and the soothing sounds of nature</span> <strong data-start=\"743\" data-end=\"760\">Trout Fishing</strong>: <span class=\"relative -mx-px my-[-0.2rem] rounded px-px py-[0.2rem] transition-colors duration-100 ease-in-out\">Anglers can indulge in fishing in the Brengi River, known for its rich trout population.</span> <span class=\"relative -mx-px my-[-0.2rem] rounded px-px py-[0.2rem] transition-colors duration-100 ease-in-out\">Fishing is permitted with prior approval from the Jammu and Kashmir Forest Department</span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"923\" data-end=\"1103\">\r\n<p data-sta