(87, 'Kashmir Tour Packages', 'SHRI AMARNATH YATRA WITH KASHMIR', 'admin@joy.com', '1', '1745666629.jpg', '<p><strong><span class=\"relative -mx-px my-[-0.2rem] rounded px-px py-[0.2rem] transition-colors duration-100 ease-in-out\">The Amarnath Cave is dedicated to Lord Shiva and is renowned for the naturally occurring ice Shiva Lingam, formed by water droplets freezing over time.</span> <span class=\"relative -mx-px my-[-0.2rem] rounded px-px py-[0.2rem] transition-colors duration-100 ease-in-out\">According to legend, Lord Shiva narrated the secret of immortality (Amar Katha) to Goddess Parvati in this cave.</span> <span class=\"relative -mx-px my-[-0.2rem] rounded px-px py-[0.2rem] transition-colors duration-100 ease-in-out\">The cave was discovered in 1850 by a Muslim shepherd, Buta Malik, who found the sacred site after receiving a bag of coal that turned into gold</span> .</strong></p>', '5', '4', 'Srinagar,Sonmarg,Baltal,DalLake', 'Srinagar International Airport', 'Srinagar International Airport', '35000', NULL, 'A journey of faith', '29000', '9906786356', '2025-04-26 06:42:41', '2025-05-31 07:06:22', '1N Srinagar', '2N Sonamarg', '1N Srinagar', 'Welcome assistance on Arrival.\r\nAccommodation in mentioned or similar hotels as per the itinerary (In base category room).\r\nAll transfers and sightseeing (Private/Independent) as per itinerary by Non AC Vehicle.\r\nAll currently applicable hotel taxes except Govt Service Tax as per prevailing rates.\r\nMeal Plan - As Per The Package.\r\nChild below 05 Years Complimentary.', 'Any expenses of personal nature like ‚Äì tips, portages, mineral water, telephone calls, laundry, Gst etc.\r\nStill / video camera fees during the tour\r\nAny flight / train ticket fare\r\nGuide service at any place\r\nSightseeing at Pahalgam (Chandanwari & Aru Valley), Sonmarg (Zero Point), Gulmarg (Chain\r\nVehcle or Drung Water Fall) or any local vehicle wherever our vehicle will not be permitted by local\r\nunion or Govt instructions.\r\n