(92, 'Kashmir Tour Packages', 'Joy Sufi Premium Tour', 'admin@joy.com', '1', '1745653274.jpg', '<p><span data-huuid=\"4750731731961633871\">Kashmir has a strong and unique relationship with Sufism,&nbsp;<mark class=\"QVRyCf\">a mystical Islamic tradition emphasizing spiritual enlightenment and devotion</mark>.&nbsp;</span><span data-huuid=\"4750731731961634208\">Sufism played a significant role in shaping the region\'s culture, promoting religious harmony, and contributing to the distinct character of Kashmiri society.&nbsp;</span><span data-huuid=\"4750731731961634545\">Kashmiri Sufism is known for its blend of Islamic teachings with elements of Hindu and Buddhist practices, resulting in a unique spiritual landscape.<span class=\"pjBG2e\" data-cid=\"989c3354-8d5e-492c-a8a9-97da20566b2f\"><span class=\"UV3uM\">&nbsp;</span></span></span></p>', '5', '4', 'Day 1: Arrive in Srinagar Welcome onboard a wonderful tour to one of the most happening destinations - Kashmir! On arrival at the Srinagar Airport- you will be welcomed & received by our representative/driver. Transfer from Airport to Hotel And check-in at the Hotel- you can relax for a while. Later in the evening- proceed for Visit. Visit Shalimar Bagh- Nishat Bagh. Enjoy shikara ride in Dal lake.,Day 2: Srinagar ‚Äì Excursion to Gulmarg (90 kms /3 ¬Ω hours one way) After Buffet Breakfast- proceed for day excursion to Gulmarg - \"Meadow of Flowers\" Arrive Gulmarg Enjoy Asia\'s Highest Cable Car Project Gulmarg Gondola - The Gondola offers all tourists scenic views of  Pir Panjal Mountains and Valley as you head towards Phase 1: KHILANMARG. You may enjoy an Sledge ride or Snow Mobile ride on the snow covered slopes (on direct payment basis) Later proceed to Srinagar. En-route visit Handloom Emporium. Arrive into Srinagar and Check In Houseboat. Dinner & Overnight stay at hotel in Srinagar.,Day 3: Srinagar to Pahalgam (90 Kms / approx 03 hrs). After Buffet Breakfast- proceed Pahalgam - Pahalgam is famous for its scenic beauty and is the jewel of the picturesque Liddar valley in the high Himalayas. It provides an ideal setting for hiking- trekking- and fishing. It is also the starting point of the annual pilgrimage to the holy cave of Amarnath. Dinner and overnight stay at the hotel in Pahalgam,Day 4: Pahalgam (Day Trip - ABC Valley Tour) - Srinagar After Buffet Breakfast proceed for ABC Valley Tour. Aru valley (Scenic meadows- Natural environment and scenery) Betaab Valley (Known for its picturesque beauty- made famous by the Bollywood movie \"Betaab\") Chandanwari (Starting point for the Amarnath Yatra and a popular hiking spot). After Valley Tour Drive to Srinagar. Dinner and overnight stay at the hotel in Srinagar Houseboat.,Day 5: Departure from Srinagar: Today after breakfast- transfer to Srinagar airport to board the return flight with Happy Memories of Joy Tours.', 'Srinagar International Airport', 'Srinagar International Airport', '98900', NULL, 'Sustainable Tour', '95900', '9906786356', '2025-04-26 07:41:14', '2025-04-26 07:41:14', '2N Srinagar', '1N Pahalgam', '1N Srinagar', 'Accommodation at hotel\r\nWelcome drink on arrival\r\nDaily breakfast and dinner\r\nNon A/C Vehicle for sightseeing\r\nAirport/Train Station Transfer\r\nAll applicable taxes', '5 % GST\r\nEntry fees to monuments and Palaces\r\nAny meals not mentioned, Any transfers, Any insurance\r\nAnything not mentioned in the inclusions', 'Travel Validity\r\nThe date is valid for travel till Tuesday, 30 September 2025.\r\n\r\nEasy Cancellation Policy\r\nIn case of more than 30 days prior to departure date, initial booking amount and any additional amount of air fare will be charged as penalty. *Less than 30 days: 50% of total tour cost will be charged as penalty.\r\n\r\nGuaranteed Dates\r\nYour selected travel dates are guaranteed in the unlikely event of a death and not due guarantee * - 12 days from your preferred dates.', NULL),
(94, 'Kashmir Tour Packages', 'Joy Delights of Kashmir', 'admin@joy.com', '1', '1745659163.jpg', '<h2 class=\"MicroComponents_curtomHighlightHeader__n6HpR undefined \r\n            \"><span class=\"  \">Trip Highlights</span></h2>\r\n<ul class=\"MicroComponents_customHighlights__fDWhp\">\r\n<li>\r\n<div class=\" MicroComponents_customHighligtsPoint__4owW3\">\r\n<p>Discover Kashmir\'s beauty from lush valleys, and the Himalayan landscapes of Gulmarg, to rich culture, serene lakes and unforgettable houseboat stays in Srinagar.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<div class=\" MicroComponents_customHighligtsPoint__4owW3\">\r\n<p>&nbsp;Explore terraced lawns, and vibrant flowers, reflecting the grandeur of Mughal architecture at Mughal Gardens in Srinagar.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<div class=\" MicroComponents_customHighligtsPoint__4owW3\">\r\n<p>Enjoy the houseboat stay on the waters of Dal Lake, surrounded by mountains and floating markets, soaking in Srinagar\'s beauty and culture.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<div class=\" MicroComponents_customHighligtsPoint__4owW3\">\r\n<p>Indulge in various adventurous&nbsp;activities amidst the Himalayan landscapes and glistening glaciers of Sonmarg.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<div class=\" MicroComponents_customHighligtsPoint__4owW3\">\r\n<p>Witness the beauty of Gulmarg, on the world\'s second-highest gondola ride and witness lush green meadows stretch as far as the eye can see.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>', '6', '5', 'DAY 1 Arrival in Srinagar | Shikara Ride at Dal Lake Welcome to Srinagar! On arrival at the Srinagar Airport- you\'ll get transferred to your hotel where you\'ll check in and rest for a while. Later in the afternoon- you\'ll be taken to Dal Lake to enjoy a scenic Shikara ride amidst the views of lush green meadows and snow-capped mountains. As you ride you can shop at the floating market or relish a cup of kahwa. Post the Shikara ride- get transferred back to your hotel for an overnight stay.,DAY 2: Srinagar Sightseeing Tour Today- you will explore the charming city of Srinagar. Start with a visit to the Mughal gardens - the serene Nishat Bagh and the historic Shalimar Bagh. Then walk through the Tulip Gardens and admire the lush beauty of the Botanical Gardens. Don\'t miss Chashme Shahi- a charming garden with refreshing natural spring water and end your tour at the Pari Mahal- offering panoramic views of Dal Lake and the surrounding mountains. Post the sightseeing- transfer to your hotel for an overnight stay.,DAY 3: Excursion to Sonmarg | Houseboat Stay in Srinagar Post check-out- start your day with a scenic drive to Sonmarg. Upon arrival- enjoy a thrilling horse ride to the Thajiwas Glacier viewpoint- for the stunning views of meadows and snow-capped mountains. After your adventure- transfer back to Srinagar and check in to your houseboat in Dal Lake for an overnight stay.,DAY 4: Transfer to Gulmarg | Day at Leisure Post check-out- get ready for a transfer to Gulmarg! Upon arrival- check in to your hotel and spend the day at leisure. You can make the most of your time in Gulmarg with a visit to The Seven Springs - Alpather Lake- Ningle Nallah- Maharani Temple and the Shrine of Baba Reshi. After the fun-filled day- head back to your hotel for an overnight stay.,DAY 5: Gulmarg Sightseeing Tour Today- get ready for a fun-filled day ahead in Gulmarg! Begin with a transfer to the Union Cab Stand to take a cab (fare not included) for a day of sightseeing. Explore the Igloo Cafe- and marvel at the Strawberry Valley and the majestic Drung Waterfall. And- don\'t forget the thrilling gondola ride to the mountaintop (at an extra cost). After the sightseeing- return to the cab stand and get transferred back to your hotel for an overnight stay,DAY 6: Departure Day This marks the end of your tour! Post check-out- you\'ll be transferred to Srinagar Airport to board your flight for an onward journey with a bag of memories and souvenirs you have bought for your 