(95, 'Kashmir Tour Packages', 'Magnificent Kashmir', 'admin@joy.com', '1', '1745660786.jpg', '<p class=\"dest-guide-header\"><span style=\"color: rgb(52, 73, 94); background-color: rgb(251, 238, 184);\"><em><strong>Your Kashmir Destination Guide</strong></em></span></p>\r\n<p>Unwind in the verdant valleys of Kashmir with this week-long vacation! Stay at a traditional houseboat in Srinagar, ride the Gulmarg Gondola and visit Pahalgam valleys.</p>\r\n<div class=\"expanded-data\">\r\n<div>\r\n<div class=\"destination-tips\">\r\n<div class=\"destination-tips-content\">\r\n<div class=\"dest-tips-header\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(251, 238, 184);\"><em><strong>what to expect</strong></em></span></div>\r\n<p class=\"dest-content\">Relax in the pleasant and cozy weather of Gulmarg. our the scenic city, enjoy sightseeing and click spectacular pictures. Relax amidst the lush landscapes of Pahalgam in the pleasant weather. Enjoy chilly evenings and explore the exciting trekking trails. Relax in the pleasant weather with temperatures between 10&deg;C and 30&deg;C in Srinagar. Indulge in sightseeing and enjoy the lively festivities.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"destination-tips-content\">\r\n<div class=\"dest-tips-header\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(251, 238, 184);\"><em><strong>Things you will love</strong></em></span></div>\r\n<p class=\"dest-content\">Sightseeing and the beautiful surroundings in Gulmarg and Soaking in lush green surroundings and exploring the various trekking trails in Pahalgam .You will also like Sightseeing and the lively festivals in Srinagar .</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', '7', '6', 'Day 1: Photoshoot in Kashmiri attire in Shikara at Dal Lake Get clicked while you pose for pictures in traditional Kashmiri attire as you ride a Shikara on Dal Lake. The breathtaking views of Dal Lake make for the perfect backdrop for your pictures. Capture fond memories of your visit and take back home a lovely picture.  Note: One photo per person is included. The photo size will be 8\" x 10\",Day 2: Gulmarg Gondola Cable Car Ride - Phase 1 (Slot 3 from 0130PM to 0330PM) Marvel at the breathtaking views of the Gulmarg mountains as you ride the famous Gondola Cable Car. Feel the rush when the cable car ascends to Kongdori Station- located 2600m above sea level. With panoramic views of majestic mountains- lush forests- and crystal clear skies- the Gondola ride offers a unique experience that is not to be missed.  Note: The activity slot is from 1:30 PM to 3:30 PM. Tickets for Phase 1 are included. Gondola tickets are subject to availability at the time of issuance.,Day 3: Riverside Lunch at Heevan Pahalgam Relish a lip-smacking lunch at the Hotel Heevan Pahalgam. Offering spectacular views of the Lidder River- it is the perfect place to unwind! Enjoy spending quality time with your loved ones as you savour yummy dishes and admire the scenery.  Note: This activity needs to be added on the day guest is reaching Pahalgam for 2N Pahalgam itinerary only,Day 5: Pahalgam to Srinagar-Lunch at Green Rooms Hotel and Shikara Ride at Dal Lake. Indulge in an authentic Kashmiri lunch at Hotel Green Rooms-renowned for its delectable local cuisine and warm service. Savour a range of dishes- from vegetarian to non-vegetarian- all crafted to delight the senses. Let the unique spices and flavors of Kashmir create a blissful culinary experience that you-ll cherish long after your visit-Enjoy a candid photoshoot session in Srinagar & capture memories of your visit. Pose with the scenic backdrop as a professional photographer clicks photos that you can cherish for a lifetime.  NOTE: 10 edited pictures will be shared. Images will be delivered 21 days after the photoshoot.,Day 6: Srinagar City Local Sightseeing Visit Local Sightseeings Like Nishat Garden-Shalimar Garden- Chashmashahi- Shrankracharya Temple- Boulevard road.,Day 7: Departure from Srinagar', 'Srinagar International Airport', 'Srinagar International Airport', '8