(98, 'Kashmir Tour Packages', 'Kashmir Tour (Jammu to Jammu)', 'admin@joy.com', '1', '1745662624.jpg', '<h4 class=\"wow fadeInUp animated\">Day : 1&nbsp;Jammu &ndash; Patnitop</h4>\r\n<p class=\"wow fadeInUp animated\">Meet and greet on arrival at Jammu Railway Station/Airport and proceed for Patnitop (4-5 hrs drive). Patnitop is set amidst beautiful surroundings. Check into the hotel. O/n Patnitop</p>\r\n<h4 class=\"wow fadeInUp animated\">Day : 2&nbsp;Patnitop &ndash; Pahalgam</h4>\r\n<p class=\"wow fadeInUp animated\">After breakfast proceed to Pahalgam (8-9 hrs drive). Pahalgam Valley Visit Saffron Field, Bat Factory, Avantipora Ruins, Apple Garden, Bat Factory, Rafting Point and Abshar Park. On arrival Leave for Baisaran Mini Switzerland.Check into the hotel. O/n Pahalgam</p>\r\n<p class=\"wow fadeInUp animated\"><strong>Day : 3 Pahalgam</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"wow fadeInUp animated\">After breakfast visit Chandanwadi - Snow point and mainly known as the starting point of sacred Amarnath yatra, Betaab valley and Aru valley by local union vehicle. Evening free for shopping and exploring local bazaar. O/n Pahalgam.</p>\r\n<h4 class=\"wow fadeInUp animated\">Day : 4&nbsp;Pahalgam &ndash; Gulmarg</h4>\r\n<p class=\"wow fadeInUp animated\">After breakfast proceed to Gulmarg (5-6 hrs drive). En route Awantipuram &ndash; Ancient Ruins, Cricket Bat factory and witness Saffron farms on both sides of the road. Check into the hotel. O/n Gulmarg.</p>\r\n<p class=\"wow fadeInUp animated\">Gulmarg has one of the best Ski slopes in the world and highest golf courses of the world with 18 holes. One can also have the view of Nanga Parbhat if weather permits. The view en route from Tangmarg to Gulmarg is fascinating.</p>\r\n<h4 class=\"wow fadeInUp animated\">Day : 5&nbsp;Gulmarg</h4>\r\n<p class=\"wow fadeInUp animated\">After breakfast walk towards Gondola rope way - Highest and longest cable car ride in India with 2 phases. Enjoy snow activities like Snow scooters, sledging, Skiing etc. at extra cost. Evening free at leisure. O/n Gulmarg.</p>\r\n<h4 class=\"wow fadeInUp animated\">Day : 6&nbsp;Gulmarg &ndash; Srinagar</h4>\r\n<p class=\"wow fadeInUp animated\">Morning after breakfast, proceed to Srinagar (2-3 hrs drive). Arrive Srinagar and check into the hotel. Later free time to enjoy near beautiful Dal Lake. O/n Srinagar.</p>\r\n<h4 class=\"wow fadeInUp animated\">Day : 7&nbsp;Srinagar &ndash; Sonmarg &ndash; Srinagar</h4>\r\n<p class=\"wow fadeInUp animated\">Today after early breakfast proceed for Sonmarg (3 hrs drive). Sonmarg is also known as Meadows of Gold. You can take a walk/ Pony ride at extra cost up to Thajwasa Glacier. Enjoy snow activities at own expenses. Back to Srinagar by evening. O/n Srinagar.</p>\r\n<h4 class=\"wow fadeInUp animated\">Day : 8&nbsp;Srinagar</h4>\r\n<p class=\"wow fadeInUp animated\">After breakfast visit famous Mughal gardens like PariMahal, Shalimar baug, Nishat baug, Chashmeshahi baug. Also visit Shankaracharya temple - Abode of Lord Shiva, from where you can have bird\'s eye view of Srinagar. O/n Srinagar.</p>\r\n<h4 class=\"wow fadeInUp animated\">Day : 9&nbsp;Srinagar &ndash; Jammu</h4>\r\n<p class=\"wow fadeInUp animated\">After breakfast proceed for Jammu (12-13 hrs drive). Reach Jammu by late evening and check into the hotel. O/n Jammu.</p>\r\n<h4 class=\"wow fadeInUp animated\">Day : 10&nbsp;Final departure</h4>\r\n<p class=\"wow fadeInUp animated\">Today drop at Jammu railway station/ airport for your onward journey. The tour ends here with the sweet memories of Joy Tour and Travels.</p>', '10', '9', 'Day 01: Pickup From Jammu Railway Station and Transfer to Patnitop City,Day 02: Patnitop City to Pahalgam Valley,Day 03: Pahalgam Valley Local Sightseeing,Day 04: Pahalgam Valley to Gulmarg Valley,Day 05: Gulmarg Valley Local Sightseeing,Day 06: Gulmarg Valley to Srinagar City,Day 07: Full Day trip to Sonamarg Valley,Day 08: Srinagar Local Sightseeing,Day 09: Transfer to Jammu City,Day 10: