(107, 'Ladakh Tour Packages', 'Joy Tremendous Ladakh + Manali Tour', 'admin@joy.com', '1', '1745920750.jpg', '<p><span data-huuid=\"3844573597977893098\">Ladakh, a high-altitude mountainous region,&nbsp;<mark class=\"QVRyCf\">offers a unique blend of natural beauty and rich cultural heritage, making it a popular tourist destination</mark>.&nbsp;</span><span data-huuid=\"3844573597977893777\">The region is known for its dramatic landscapes, including high-altitude deserts, stunning lakes like Pangong Tso, and majestic mountains and </span><span data-huuid=\"3844573597977894456\">also renowned for its Buddhist monasteries and the vibrant Ladakhi culture, which provides a glimpse into the region\'s history and traditions.<span class=\"pjBG2e\" data-cid=\"b3180985-926b-4baa-88ca-9f5713e67f1d\"><span class=\"UV3uM\">&nbsp;</span></span></span></p>', '11', '10', 'Day : 1 Arrival at Srinagar Airport,Day : 2 Srinagar ‚Äì Kargil,Day : 3 Kargil ‚Äì Leh,Day : 4 Leh City Sightseeing,Day : 5 Leh ‚Äì Nubra Valley,Day : 6 Nubra valley - Leh,Day : 7 Leh ‚Äì Pangong Lake ‚Äì Leh,Day : 8 Leh ‚Äì Jispa,Day : 9 Jispa ‚Äì Manali,Day : 10 Manali ‚Äì Chandigarh,Day  : 11 Drop at Chandigarh Airport', 'Srinagar Airport', 'Kushok Bakula Rimpochee Airport', '50000', NULL, 'Special offer', '45000', '9906786356', '2025-04-29 09:59:10', '2025-04-29 09:59:10', '1N Sgr, 1N Kargil, 4N Leh', '1N Nubra Valley, 1N Jispa', '1N Manali, 1N Chandigarh', 'Accommodation at hotel\r\nWelcome drink on arrival\r\nDaily breakfast and dinner\r\nNon A/C Vehicle for sightseeing\r\nAirport/Train Station Transfer\r\nAll applicable taxes', '5 % GST\r\nEntry fees to monuments and Palaces\r\nAny meals not mentioned, Any transfers, Any insurance\r\nAnything not mentioned in the inclusions', 'Travel Validity\r\nThe date is valid for travel till Tuesday, 30 September 2025.\r\n\r\nEasy Cancellation Policy\r\nIn case of more than 30 days prior to departure date, initial booking amount and any additional amount of air fare wi