(112, 'Kashmir Tour Packages', 'JOY KASHMIR WITH TAJ VIVANTA', 'admin@joy.com', '1', '1746095949.jpg', '<div class=\"th-itinerary-day-number\"><strong>Day 01:&nbsp;Arrival in Srinagar | Transfer to Pahalgam Valley.| Pahalgam Sightseeing Tour.</strong></div>\r\n<p>Welcome to Srinagar! Upon arrival at the airport, you&rsquo;ll be transferred to your hotel in Pahalgam. Check in and take some rest. Later, get transferred to the Union Cab Stand, from where you can take the cab (at an additional cost) to explore the famous Aru Valley, Betaab Valley, and Chandanwari and soak in the views of the stunning scenery. After a wonderful day, reach the Union Cab Stand on your own, from where you will get transferred back to the hotel for an overnight stay.</p>\r\n<div class=\"th-itinerary-day-number\"><strong>Day 02:&nbsp;Transfer to Srinagar City| Srinagar Sightseeing Tour.</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"th-itinerary-day-number\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"th-itinerary-day-number\">After checking out of your hotel, you\'ll be transferred to Srinagar. Upon arrival, check in and relax for a while. Then, get ready to explore Shalimar Bagh, a Mughal garden with terraces and cascading fountains. Visit the Shankaracharya Temple, an ancient site dedicated to Lord Shiva. Continue to Chashme Shahi, a garden with freshwater springs believed to have medicinal properties. Unwind with a Shikara ride on Dal Lake, renowned for its unique floating market and traditional houseboats.</div>\r\n<div class=\"th-itinerary-day-number\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"th-itinerary-day-number\">\r\n<div class=\"th-itinerary-head\">\r\n<div class=\"th-itinerary-head--left-section\">\r\n<div class=\"top-section \">\r\n<div class=\"th-itinerary-day-number\"><strong>Day 03: Excursion to Gulmarg Valley.</strong></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"th-itinerary-head--right-section\">\r\n<div class=\"action-block action-block__open\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"accordion\">\r\n<div cla