inerary-day-content\">\r\n<div class=\"th-itinerary-day-description\"><span class=\"th-raw-html \">After checking out of the hotel, you\'ll be transferred to Sonmarg. Spend the day exploring this beautiful valley surrounded by snow-capped mountains. First, get driven to Sonmarg Pony Ride Parking. From there, take a horseback ride to Thajiwas Glacier and be captivated by the ice formations and lush green meadows. You can also experience the adrenaline rush of whitewater rafting on the Sindh River (available at an additional cost). Later, check in to your houseboat for an overnight stay.</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"th-itinerary-day-description\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"th-itinerary-day-description\">\r\n<div class=\"th-itinerary-head\">\r\n<div class=\"th-itinerary-head--left-section\">\r\n<div class=\"top-section \">\r\n<div class=\"th-itinerary-day-number\"><strong>Day 05:&nbsp;Departure Day.</strong></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"th-itinerary-head--right-section\">\r\n<div class=\"action-block action-block__open\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"accordion\">\r\n<div class=\"Collapsible\"><span id=\"collapsible-trigger-1746095588960\" class=\"Collapsible__trigger is-open\" role=\"button\" aria-expanded=\"true\" aria-disabled=\"false\" aria-controls=\"collapsible-content-1746095588960\"></span>\r\n<div id=\"collapsible-content-1746095588960\" class=\"Collapsible__contentOuter\" role=\"region\" aria-labelledby=\"collapsible-trigger-1746095588960\">\r\n<div class=\"Collapsible__contentInner\">\r\n<div class=\"th-itinerary-day-content\">\r\n<div class=\"th-itinerary-day-description\"><span class=\"th-raw-html \">In the morning, check out of your hotel and get transferred to Srinagar Airport/Railway Station for an onward journey back home. This marks the end of your trip.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<