(119, 'Ladakh Tour Packages', 'Romantic Ladakh Holiday', 'admin@joy.com', '1', '1746433249.jpg', '<p>Located at an altitude of 14,200 feet, Pangong Lake, also known as Pangong Tso, stretches from India to China. The crystal clear waters of the Pangong Lake change its color in many shades of blue and green with the changing position of the sun in the sky. A refreshing phenomenon and a sheer treat for eyes, the lake is a beautiful contrast of deep blue water against the strong hues of brown land. Though the brackish water supports negligible vegetation or aquatic life, the lake is also a haven for bird watchers. Inner Line Permit is required to visit here which can now be availed online as well. Also, this high grassland lake has made an appearance in several Indian movies.</p>', '08', '07', 'Arrival in Leh,Sunset at Shanti Stupa- Private Transfers,Leh to Nubra Valley,Sightseeing in Nubra Valley,Nubra Valley to Leh,Sightseeing in Leh,Departure from Leh', 'Leh Airport', 'Leh Airport', '38950', NULL, 'Holiday Package', '27950', '9906786356', '2025-05-05 08:20:49', '2025-05-05 08:20:49', 'Leh/Sham Valley/Nubra/Khardung La', 'Pangong Lake', 'Hunder-Turtuk/Shyok ‚Äì', 'Accommodation at hotel\r\nWelcome drink on arrival\r\nDaily breakfast and dinner\r\nNon A/C Vehicle for sightseeing\r\nAirport/Train Station Transfer\r\nAll applicable taxes', '5 % GST\r\nEntry fees to monuments and Palaces\r\nAny meals not mentioned, Any transfers, Any insurance\r\nAnything not mentioned in the inclusions', 'Travel Validity\r\nThe date is valid for travel till Tuesday, 30 September 2025.\r\n\r\nEasy Cancellation Policy\r\nIn case of more than 30 days prior to departure date, initial booking amount and any additional amount of air fare will be charged as penalty. *Less than 30 days: 50% of total tour cost will be charged as penalty.\r\n\r\nGuaranteed Dates\r\nYour selected travel dates are guaranteed in the unlikely event of a death and not due guarantee * - 12 days from your preferred dates