(120, 'Ladakh Tour Packages', 'Incredible Leh & Ladakh Package 05 Nights 06 Days', 'admin@joy.com', '1', '1746439159.jpg', '<div class=\"MicroComponents_customHightlightWrapper__z2o50 undefined\">\r\n<ul class=\"MicroComponents_customHighlights__fDWhp\">\r\n<li>\r\n<div class=\" MicroComponents_customHighligtsPoint__4owW3\">\r\n<p>Have a vacation in the two most amazing destinations in India- Leh and Ladakh, blending fun and adventure with scenic landscapes and stunning peaks.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<div class=\" MicroComponents_customHighligtsPoint__4owW3\">\r\n<p>Enjoy an extraordinary adventure as you take the Bactrian camel ride and transverse through the white sands of the stunning Nubra Valley desert.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<div class=\" MicroComponents_customHighligtsPoint__4owW3\">\r\n<p>Admire the beauty of Pangong Lake, where the colours of the Himalayan peaks reflect in its shimmering waters, offering a beautiful and eye-pleasing view.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<div class=\" MicroComponents_customHighligtsPoint__4owW3\">\r\n<p>Experience firsthand a blend of innovation and education as you explore SECMOL, the school that became famous because of the popular movie- 3 Idiots.&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<div class=\" MicroComponents_customHighligtsPoint__4owW3\">\r\n<p>Take-in the views of tall Himalayan peaks as you conquer the legendary Khardung La Pass, one of the world\'s tallest all-season motorable passes.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"tour-page-itinerary-group\">\r\n<div class=\"Itinerary_itineraryWrapper__phB2v  \">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>', '06', '05', 'Arrival in Leh | Leh Sightseeing Tour,Day Tour to Sham Valley | The Mysterious Paths of Ladakh,Transfer to Nubra Valley via Khardung La Pass | Exploring the Cold Desert,Transfer to Pangong Tso | Camping at the Pangong Tso,Transfer to Leh | Driving Through the Majestic Chang La Pass,Departure Day', 'Leh Airport', 'Leh Airport', '29000', NULL, 'Journey To The Land Of Lamas', '23000', '9906786356', '2025-05-05 09:59:19', '2025-05-05 09:59:19', 'Leh', 'Nubra Valley', 'Pangong Tso', 'Accommodation at hotel\r\nWelcome drink on arrival\r\nDaily breakfast and dinner\r\nNon A/C Vehicle for sightseeing\r\nAirport/Train Station Transfer\r\nAll applicable taxes', '5 % GST\r\nEntry fees to monuments and Palaces\r\nAny meals not mentioned, Any transfers, Any insurance\r\nAnything not mentioned in the inclusions', 'Travel Validity\r\nThe date is valid for travel till Tuesday, 30 September 2025.\r\n\r\nEasy Cancellation Policy\r\nIn case of more than 30 days prior to departure date, initial booking amount and any additional amount of air fare will be charged as penalty. *Less than 30 days: 50% of total tour cost will be charged as penalty.\r\n\r\nGuaranteed Dates\r\nYour selected travel dates are guaranteed in the unlikely event of a death and not due guarantee * - 12 days from your preferred dates.', NULL),
(121, 'Ladakh Tour Packages', '07 Nights 08 Days Leh Ladakh with Manali', 'admin@joy.com', '1', '1746440602.jpg', '<ul class=\"product-overview__list\">\r\n<li class=\"product-overview__list-item\">\r\n<div>\r\n<p>Enjoy this beautiful amalgamation of beautiful Himachal valleys and thrilling Ladakh routes in a single tour</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"product-overview__list-item\">\r\n<div>\r\n<p>Experience Himalyan region with utmost safety and comfort in well sanitised accommodation and vehicles</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"product-overview__list-item\">\r\n<div>\r\n<p>Visit SECMOL, The real 3-idiots school founded by Dr. Sonam Wangchuk</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"product-overview__list-item\">\r\n<div>\r\n<p>Let the adrenaline rush pump through your veins as you drive through the world&rsquo;s highest motorable passes like Khardung la and lachung la, rohtang la, and Baralacha la</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"product-overview__list-item\">\r\n<div>\r\n<p>Visit pangong lake; world&rsquo;s highest saltwater lake that changes its colour from shades of blue to green to red</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>', '08', '07', 'Arrival in Leh | Welcome to the Top of the World,Sham Valley Excursion | Visit the Famous 3-Idiots School,Leh to Nubra Valley via Khardung-La Pass | A Drive to The World‚Äôs Highest All Season Motorable Road (18000 ft.),Nubra valley to Pangong Lake | Recreate the Famous Bollywood Moments,Pangong Lake to Leh | Excursion to Rancho School,Leh to Sarchu | Witness the Beauty of Barren Lands,Sarchu to Manali | Feel being transported to Another World,Day at Leisure and Departure from Manali | End of Trip With a Bag Full of Life Time Memories', 'Leh Airport', 'Manali Station', '67000', NULL, 'Free Excursion to Rancho School', '55000', '9906786356', '2025-05-05 10:23:22', '2025-05-05 10:23:22', 'leh/sham valley/nubra', 'Pangong/Rancho school', 'Sarchu/Manali', 'Accommodation at hotel\r\nWelcome drink on arrival\r\nDaily breakfas