(122, 'Ladakh Tour Packages', 'Let\'s travel Beyond Boundaries with Bike Adventure', 'admin@joy.com', '1', '1746442252.jpg', '<div class=\"itinerary-day-v2__day-description\">\r\n<p><strong>Day 01 I Arrival at Srinagar Airport&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<p>Upon your arrival, the driver will transfer you from the airport to your pre-booked hotel. Once you check-in, the remaining day is yours to enjoy, rejuvenate, and adjust to the weather conditions. Please note it is necessary to acclimatize to the cold weather and altitude of the region so that you are ready for the adventures in Leh Ladakh.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Day 02 I Srinagar to Kargil&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<p>After a delicious breakfast, collect your bike post-briefing at the hotel and head to Kargil. Drive through the Zoji La pass and admire the scenic views of Tiger Hill &amp; other famous Himalayan peaks. We will take a small stopover to the Kargil War Memorial and pay your respect to martyrs of the Kargil War on the way. Have an overnight stay in the pre-booked hotel in Kargil.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Day 03 I Kargil to Leh&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;Check out from your hotel and leave for Leh. Pass through the Lamayuru village to reach Basgo Palace &amp; Monastery. After that, take a small break at the Sangam viewpoint &amp; see the confluence of the Zanskar &amp; Indus Rivers. Next, ride the Magnetic Hill, a road that defies the law of gravity. Later, visit the Hall of Fame and pay tribute to martyrs of Indo-Pak wars. Enjoy an overnight stay at your pre-booked hotel in Leh.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Day 04 I Leh Local Sightseeing</strong></p>\r\n<p>Go on a local sightseeing tour of Leh on your bike. Visit the popular Shanti Stupa and admire the breathtaking views of the city from the clifftop. Head toward the Leh Palace built in the 17th century. Explore the local Leh Market, shop for some Tibetan handicrafts &amp; enjoy delicious Ladakhi cuisine. Post-sightseeing tour, ride back to your hotel for an overnight stay in Leh.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Day 05 I Leh to Nubra Valley via Khardung-La Pass</strong></p>\r\n<p>Check out from your hotel and leave for the Nubra Valley. Ride through the Khardung-La Pass the world\'s all-season highest navigable road. Arrive at Nubra Valley and take in the scenic views of the white sand desert. If time permits stop and gaze at the Diskit Monastery. Enjoy a double-humped Bactrian Camel Ride in the region. Spend a memorable night at the pre-booked camp in Nubra Valley.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Day 06 I Nubra Valley to Pangong Lake&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<p>Check out from your campsite and drive to Pangong Lake. Enjoy traveling to this beautiful lake nestled on the Indo-China border. Admire the scenic views of changing colors from shades of blue to green to red as you reach Pangong Tso, one of the highest-altitude lakes. Take in the views of the Shyok River &amp; mountains on your way to Pangong Lake. Have an overnight stay at your pre-booked campsite near Pangong Lake.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Day 07 I Pangong Lake to Leh</strong></p>\r\n<p>Check out from your campsite and leave for Leh. Take a stopover at the Chang-la Pass which is known as one of the world\'s highest mountain passes. Visit famous places like Changla Baba Temple &amp; Druk Padma School during the tour. You can also explore the beautiful Thiksey Monastery on the way. Post your sightseeing tour, hand over your bike at the hotel, and enjoy an overnight stay in Leh.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Day 08 I Departure From Leh</strong></p>\r\n<p>Pack your bags and check out from your hotel in Leh. The driver will pick you up from the hotel and take you to Leh Airport from where your exhilarating 6 day-tour will come to an end and connect onward journey with great memories of Joy Tour and Travels.<br>.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div class=\"itinerary-day-v2__images-row\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"itinerary-day-v2__images-row\">&nbsp;</div>', '8', '7', 'Day 01: Arrival in Srinagar | Welcome to the Heaven on the Earth,Day 02: Srinagar to Kargil | Visit Coldest Inhabited Place in the World,Day 03: Kargil to Leh | Visit the Beautiful Sham Valley,Day 04: Leh Local Sightseeing | Explore The Heart of Ladakh,Day 05: Leh to Nubra Valley via Khardung-La Pass | Ride through World‚Äôs Highest Motorable Road (18000 ft.),Day 06: Nubra Valley to Pangong Lake | Visit World\'s Highest Salt Lake,Day 07: Pangong Lake to Leh | Visit World\'s One of the Highest Mountain Passes,Day 08: Departure From Leh | Bid Adieu to the White Desert of India', 'Srinagar Airport', 'Kushok Bakula Rimpochee Airport', '38950', NULL, '\"In the land of leh every step is a Journey into the soul\"', '27950', '9906786356', '2025-05-05 10:50:52', '2025-05-05 10:50:52', '01 N Kargil,04 N Leh', '01 N Nubra', '01 N Pangong', 'Accommodation at hotel\r\nWelcome drink on arrival\r\nDaily breakfast and dinner\r\nNon A/C Vehicle for sightseeing\r\nAirport/Train Station Transfer\r\nAll applicable taxes', '5 % GST\r\nEntry fees to monuments and Palaces\r\nAny meals not mentioned, Any transfers, Any insurance\r\nAnything not mentioned in the inclusions', 'Travel Validity\r\nThe date is valid for travel till Tuesday, 30 September 2025.\r\n\r\nEasy Cancellation Policy\r\nIn case of more than 30 days prior to departure date, initial booking amount and any additional amount of air fare will be charged as penalty. *Less than 30 days: 50% of total tour cost will be charged as penalty.\r\n\r\nGuaranteed Dates\r\nYour selected travel dates are guaranteed in the unlikely event of a death and not due guarantee * - 12 days from your preferred dates.', NULL);
