(126, 'Kashmir Tour Packages', 'Exclusive Joy Package', 'admin@joy.com', '1', '1746609861.jpg', '<div class=\"MicroComponents_customHightlightWrapper__z2o50 undefined\">\r\n<h2 class=\"MicroComponents_curtomHighlightHeader__n6HpR undefined \r\n            \"><span class=\"  \">Trip Highlights</span></h2>\r\n<ul class=\"MicroComponents_customHighlights__fDWhp\">\r\n<li>\r\n<div class=\" MicroComponents_customHighligtsPoint__4owW3\">\r\n<p>Explore Kashmir, from Srinagar\'s Dal Lake to Pahalgam\'s lush valleys and Gulmarg\'s snow-capped peaks, in a journey through nature&rsquo;s paradise.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<div class=\" MicroComponents_customHighligtsPoint__4owW3\">\r\n<p>Create beautiful memories with your partner on a shikara ride on Dal Lake in Srinagar while enjoying breathtaking views of the surroundings.&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<div class=\" MicroComponents_customHighligtsPoint__4owW3\">\r\n<p>Explore the popular Bollywood filming location of Pahalgam, the Betaab Valley, offering stunning views of the Lidder River and lush landscapes.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<div class=\" MicroComponents_customHighligtsPoint__4owW3\">\r\n<p>Take the Gulmarg Gondola, one of the highest cable cars in the world, offering panoramic views of the snow-capped peaks of the Himalayas.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<div class=\" MicroComponents_customHighligtsPoint__4owW3\">\r\n<p>Witness the stunning beauty of Thajiwas Glacier, a snow-clad wonder nestled in Sonmarg, offering a surreal blend of icy landscapes and alpine meadows.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"tour-page-itinerary-group\">\r\n<div class=\"Itinerary_itineraryWrapper__phB2v  \">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>', '8', '7', 'DAY 1 Arrival in Srinagar | Shikara Ride on Dal Lake | Houseboat Stay Upon arrival at Srinagar Airport you\'ll be transferred to the picturesque Dal Lake surrounded by the breathtaking Himalayan peaks. Embark on a shikara ride while taking in the mesmerizing views of vibrant floating gardens houseboats and the distant snow-capped mountains. Afterward check in to your traditional houseboat- where you can relax while experiencing the Kashmiri hospitality with an overnight stay on the lake.,DAY 2 Srinagar Sightseeing Tour Check out from your houseboat and get driven to your hotel in Srinagar. Post check in- get driven for a city tour- starting with the famous Mughal gardens. Stroll through Nishat Bagh- where terraced lawns overlook Dal Lake with stunning views of the Zabarwan mountains. Next- visit other sites like Chashme Shahi- a royal spring garden & the ancient Shankaracharya Temple- offering panoramic views of the city. Later- explore the bustling markets of Lal Chowk before being driven back to the hotel.,DAY 3 Excursion to Sonmarg In the morning- get transferred for a day trip to Sonmarg. From Thajiwas Pony Stand- you can take a horse ride to the Thajiwas Glacier viewpoint- surrounded by lush meadows- streams- and the majestic Himalayas. If time permits- you can visit the stunning Krishnasar Lake with its crystal-clear waters reflecting the mountains- or opt for an exciting rafting experience on the Sindh River (at an additional cost). From pony stand- you\'ll be driven back to the hotel.,DAY 4 Arrival in Pahalgam | Pahalgam Sightseeing Tour Today- check out and get transferred to your hotel in Pahalgam. After checking in- head to the Pahalgam union cab stand- where you can hire a cab (fare not included) to explore the area\'s scenic spots. Discover the breathtaking beauty of Aru Valley- Betaab Valley- and Chandanwari- known for their stunning landscapes and serene surroundings. After your visit- return to the cab stand on your own and then get transferred back to your hotel for an overnight stay.,DAY 5 Day at Leisure in Pahalgam Spend the day at leisure- either relaxing at your hotel or exploring the charming town of Pahalgam at your own pace. You can visit attractions like Poshwan Park- offering peaceful green spaces or the scenic Baisaran Valley- often called \"Mini Switzerland\" for its lush meadows. You can also take a trip to the Tulian Lake or enjoy a fun-filled day at Lidder Amusement Park. For adventure enthusiasts- rafting on the Lidder River is also an option. Later- return to the hotel for an overnight stay.,DAY 6 Transfer to Gulmarg | Day at Leisure After checking out- you‚Äôll be transferred to your hotel in Gulmarg. Once you check in- the rest of the day is yours to enjoy at leisure. You can explore nearby attractions like the Gulmarg Children‚Äôs Park- perfect for a relaxing stroll- the historic Maharani Temple- or the peaceful Shrine of Baba Reshi. Additionally- you can take a day trip to the Gulmarg Biosphere Reserve to discover its rich flora and fauna. Later return to your hotel for a comfortable overnight stay.,DAY 7 Gulmarg Sightseeing Tour In the morning- get ready to board your transfer to Gulmarg Union Cab Stand- from where you can take a cab to explore Gulmarg. Visit attractions like Strawberry Valley and Drung Waterfall. Then- treat yourself to a delicious lunch at Igloo Cafe (at your own cost). Also- enjoy a ride on the famous Gulmarg Gondola (at your own cost). Later- head back to the Union Cab Stand by yourself from where you will get transferred back to the hotel for an overnight stay.,DAY 8 Departure Today check-out & get transferred to the Srinagar airport as you say goodbye to the beautiful town of Gulmarg. This is where your trip ends.', 'Srinagar International Airport', 'Srinagar International Airport', '47000', NULL, 'Journey Through Mountains & Meadows', '39900', '9906786356', '2025-05-07 09:24:21', '2025-05-07 09:24:21', '4N Srinagar', '2N Pahalgam', '2N Gulmarg', 'Accommodation at hotel\r\nWelcome drink on arrival\r\nDaily breakfast and dinner\r\nNon A/C Vehicle for sightseeing\r\nAirport/Train Station Transfer\r\nAll applicable taxes', '5 % GST\r\nEntry fees to monuments and Palaces\r\nAny meals not mentioned, Any transfers, Any insurance\r\nAnything not mentioned in the inclusions', 'Travel Validity\r\nThe date is valid for travel till Tuesday, 30 September 2025.\r\n\r\nEasy Cancellation Policy\r\nIn case of more than 30 days prior to departure date, initial booking amount and any additional amount of air fare will be charged as penalty. *Less than 30 days: 50% of total tour cost will be charged as penalty.\r\n\r\nGuaranteed Dates\r\nYour selected travel dates are guaranteed in the unlikely event of a death and not due guarantee * - 12 days from your preferred dates.', NULL),
(127, 'Kashmir Tour Packages', 'Uncover Kashmir | Journey to Nature Paradise', 'admin@joy.com', '1', '1746611284.jpg', '<h2 class=\"MicroComponents_curtomHighlightHeader__n6HpR undefined \r\n            \"><span class=\"  \">Trip Highlights</span></h2>\r\n<ul class=\"MicroComponents_customHighlights__fDWhp\">\r\n<li>\r\n<div class=\" MicroComponents_customHighligtsPoint__4owW3\">\r\n<p>Discover Kashmir, from the lush gardens and houseboats of Srinagar to the picturesque beauty of Pahalgam&rsquo;s meadows and valleys.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<div class=\" MicroComponents_customHighligtsPoint__4owW3\">\r\n<p>Experience the unique charm of staying in a traditional houseboat on Dal Lake, offering a cozy retreat with stunning views of the water and mountains.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<div class=\" MicroComponents_customHighligtsPoint__4owW3\">\r\n<p>Take a ride on the Gulmarg Gondola, one of the highest cable cars in the world and marvel at the panoramic views of snow-capped peaks and verdant valleys.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<div class=\" MicroComponents_customHighligtsPoint__4owW3\">\r\n<p>Glide across the waters of Dal Lake in a Shikara boat and be amazed by the picturesque views of the surrounding mountains, lush floating gardens and vibrant houseboats.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>', '4', '3', 'DAY 1 Arrival in Srinagar | Transfer to Pahalgam Welcome to Srinagar! Upon arrival at the airport- you\'ll be driven to Pahalgam. Upon arrival- check in at the hotel and later- get driven to the Pahalgam Union Cab Stand. Hire a cab (at your own cost) and visit various place like Aru Valley- a pristine location known for its lush meadows. Also explore the Betaab Valley- named after the famous Bollywood movie \"Betaab\". Also- get a chance to explore Chandanwari. Later- get transferred from the union cab stand to the hotel for an overnight stay.,DAY 2 Transfer to Srinagar | Srinagar Sightseeing Tour | Shikara Ride on Dal Lake Check out from the hotel and board the transfer to Srinagar. Upon arrival- check in at your hotel. Later- enjoy a sightseeing tour of Srinagar- visiting highlights such as Shalimar Bagh- Nishat Bagh- and Chashme Shahi- each showcasing beautiful Mughal garden architecture. Visit other attractions before heading to the Dal Lake- where you\'ll enjoy a scenic and popular Shikara Boat ride. Later- you\'ll be driven back to the hotel for an overnight stay.,DAY 3 Day Trip to Gulmarg | Srinagar Houseboat Stay Check out from the hotel and get transferred to Gulmarg Union Cab Stand. Upon arrival- you can walk or take a cab to the Gondola cable car station. Enjoy a ride on the famous Gulmarg Gondola- one of the highest cable cars in the world. You can even visit various sites such as Strawberry Valley- Drung Waterfall- and Igloo Cafe. Afterward- return to the Union Cab Stand and get driven to your houseboat in Srinagar. Check in and enjoy your overnight stay.,DAY 4 Departure In the morning- check out from your houseboat and get transferred to the Srinagar Airport. This is where your trip comes to an end.', 'Srinagar International Airport', 'Srinagar International Airport', '15999', NULL, 'Sustainable Tour', '12999', '9906786356', '2025-05-07 09:48:04', '2025-05-07 09:48:04', '1N Srinagar', '1N Pahalgam', '1N Dal Lake', 'Accommodation at hotel\r\nWelcome drink on arrival\r\nDaily breakfast and dinner\r\nNon A/C Vehicle for sightseeing\r\nAirport/Train Station Transfer\r\nAll applicable taxes', '5 % GST\r\nEntry fees to monuments and Palaces\r\nAny meals not mentioned, Any transfers, Any insurance\r\nAnything not mentioned in the inclusions', 'Travel Validity\r\nThe date is valid for travel till Tuesday, 30 September 2025.\r\n\r\nEasy Cancellation Policy\r\nIn case of more than 30 days prior to departure date, initial booking amount and any additional amount of air fare will be charged as penalty. *Less than 30 days: 50% of total tour cost will be charged as penalty.\r\n\r\nGuaranteed Dates\r\nYour selected travel dates are guaranteed in the unlikely event of a death and not due guarantee * - 12 days from your preferred dates.', NULL),
(128, 'Ladakh Tour Packages', 'Wonders of Ladakh | FREE Inner Line Permits', 'admin@joy.com', '1', '1746612032.jpg', '<p>Get ready for the most adventurous drive-through of your life. This tour lets you explore both the beauty of Manali and the thrills of Ladakh, and going through the cultural side of Leh makes the tour even more interesting. The unlimited fun activities in Manali, driving through the hairpin bends of the route, and exploring the heart of Ladakh; are the experiences that make this tour full of crazy and unique experiences.</p>', '10', '09', 'Arrival at Delhi and Transfer to Manali | Gateway to The Land of High Passes,Arrival at Manali | Land of Scenic Beauty,Manali To Jispa | Drive Through Atal Tunnel to Enter A Different World,Jispa To Sarchu Via Baralacha-la | A Night Under Starlit Sky,Sarchu to Leh | Drive Through Gata Loops,21 Hairpin Bends,Leh Local Sightseeing | Soak in the Vibrant Ladakhi Culture,Leh to Nubra Valley via Khardung-La Pass | A Drive to the World‚Äôs Highest Motorable Road (18000 ft.),Nubra Valley to Pangong Lake | Recreate The Famous Bollywood Moments,Pangong Lake to Leh | Excursion to Rancho School,Departure | It\'s Time to say Goodbye to the Mountains', 'Delhi Airport', 'Leh Airport', '77000', NULL, 'Adventurous Ladakh', '65000', '9906786356', '2025-05-07 10:00:32', '2025-05-07 10:00:32', 'manali/jispa', 'sarchu/leh', 'Nubra/pangong', 'Accommodation at hotel\r\nWelcome drink on arrival\r\nDaily breakfast and dinner\r\nNon A/C Vehicle for sightseeing\r\nAirport/Train Station Transfer\r\nAll applicable taxes', '5 % GST\r\nEntry fees to monuments and Palaces\r\nAny meals not mentioned, Any transfers, Any insurance\r\nAnything not mentioned in the inclusions', 'Travel Validity\r\nThe date is valid for travel till Tuesday, 30 September 2025.\r\n\r\nEasy Cancellation Policy\r\nIn case of more than 30 days prior to departure date, initial booking amount and any additional amount of air fare will be charged as penalty. *Less than 30 days: 50% of total tour cost will be charged as penalty.\r\n\r\nGuaranteed Dates\r\nYour selected travel dates are guaranteed in the unlikely event of a death and not due guarantee * - 12 days from your preferred dates.', NULL),
(129, 'Kashmir Tour Packages', 'Valley of Dreams- Nigeen Lake Tour', 'admin@joy.com', '1', '1746612483.jpg', '<h2 class=\"MicroComponents_curtomHighlightHeader__n6HpR undefined \r\n            \"><span class=\"  \">Trip Highlights</span></h2>\r\n<ul class=\"MicroComponents_customHighlights__fDWhp\">\r\n<li>\r\n<div class=\" MicroComponents_customHighligtsPoint__4owW3\">\r\n<p>Discover the beauty of Kashmir, exploring Pahalgam&rsquo;s lush valleys and Srinagar&rsquo;s iconic Dal Lake and Mughal gardens - a perfect mix of natural splendor and cultural richness.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<div class=\" MicroComponents_customHighligtsPoint__4owW3\">\r\n<p>Immerse yourself in the scenic beauty and admire Gulmarg\'s picturesque landscapes, which have served as a backdrop for several Bollywood and international films.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<div class=\" MicroComponents_customHighligtsPoint__4owW3\">\r\n<p>Visit the ancient Shankaracharya Temple situated on the Zabarwan Range, offering stunning panoramic views of Srinagar City from its strategic location.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<div class=\" MicroComponents_customHighligtsPoint__4owW3\">\r\n<p>Glide across the famous Dal Lake on a Shikara, a traditional Kashmiri boat, surrounded by floating markets, lush gardens, and iconic houseboats.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<div class=\" MicroComponents_customHighligtsPoint__4owW3\">\r\n<p>Admire the breathtaking white marble architecture of the Hazratbal Shrine, blending Mughal and Persian styles&mdash;a true symbol of unity and spirituality in Kashmir.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>', '4', '3', 'DAY 1 Arrival in Srinagar | Transfer to Pahalgam | Sightseeing Tour Upon arrival at Srinagar airport- get transferred to your hotel in Pahalgam & check-in. Later get driven to the Pahalgam Union Cab Stand- where you can hire a cab (at your own cost) to explore the iconic valleys of Pahalgam. Visit Aru Valley & Chandanwari- renowned for the breathtaking landscapes- & unwind by the riverbanks in Betaab Valley. If you\'re feeling adventurous- try rafting on Lidder River (additional cost) before returning to the cab stand. From there get driven back to the hotel.,DAY 2 Transfer to Srinagar | Sightseeing Tour | Shikara Ride at Dal Lake Today check out from the hotel & get driven to Srinagar. Upon arrival check in & relax before embarking on a sightseeing tour of the city. Visit the Shalimar Bagh- a stunning Mughal garden & Chashme Shahi- famed for its refreshing springs. Next- explore the Hazratbal Shrine- a revered religious site & the historic Shankaracharya Temple- offering breathtaking views of the valley. Next- enjoy a Shikara ride on Dal Lake- admiring the surroundings. Afterwards- get transferred back to the hotel.,DAY 3 Day Trip to Gulmarg | Overnight Houseboat Stay Today- check out & get transferred to the Gulmarg Union Cab Stand. Upon arrival- hire a cab (at your own cost) for your Gulmarg sightseeing tour. Explore at your own pace visiting the Drung Waterfall known for its serene beauty & enjoy a thrilling ride on the famous Gulmarg Gondola (additional cost). Afterward return to the cab stand & get driven to your hotel in Srinagar to pick up your bags. Afterwards get driven to Nigeen Lake. where you\'ll check in to stay overnight on a houseboat.,DAY 4 Departure In the morning- check out from the houseboat and get transferred to the Srinagar Airport for your onward journey. This marks the end of your trip.', 'Srinagar International Airport', 'Srinagar International Airport', '16999', NULL, 'Memorable Trip', '13999', '9906786356', '2025-05-07 10:08:03', '2025-05-07 10:08:03', '1N Pahalgam', '1N Srinagar', '1N Nigeen Lake', 'Accommodation at hotel\r\nWelcome drink on arrival\r\nDaily breakfast and dinner\r\nNon A/C Vehicle for sightseeing\r\nAirport/Train Station Transfer\r\nAll applicable taxes', '5 % GST\r\nEntry fees to monuments and Palaces\r\nAny meals not mentioned, Any transfers, Any insurance\r\nAnything 