(130, 'Kashmir Tour Packages', 'Joy Jannat e Kashmir', 'admin@joy.com', '1', '1746612998.jpg', '<p>Escape to the serene beauty of Kashmir with our specially curated 5-day tour package. Witness snow-capped mountains, shimmering lakes, colorful gardens, and experience the warm hospitality of the Kashmiri people. Ideal for couples, families, and nature lovers!</p>', '05', '04', 'Srinagar,Gulmarg,Sonmarg,Pahalgam', 'Srinagar International Airport', 'Srinagar International Airport', '20000', NULL, 'with shikara ride', '15000', '9906786356', '2025-05-07 10:16:38', '2025-05-31 07:42:48', '2N Srinagar', '1N DalLake', '1N Srinagar', 'Accommodation at hotel\r\nWelcome drink on arrival\r\nDaily breakfast and dinner\r\nNon A/C Vehicle for sightseeing\r\nAirport/Train Station Transfer\r\nAll applicable taxes', '5 % GST\r\nEntry fees to monuments and Palaces\r\nAny meals not mentioned, Any transfers, Any insurance\r\nAnything not mentioned in the inclusions', 'Travel Validity\r\nThe date is valid for travel till Tuesday, 30 September 2025.\r\n\r\nEasy Cancellation Policy\r\nIn case of more than 30 days prior to departure date, initial booking amount and any additional amount of air fare will be charged as penalty. *Less than 30 days: 50% of total tour cost will be charged as penalty.\r\n\r\nGuaranteed Dates\r\nYour selected travel dates are guaranteed in the unlikely event of a death and not due guarantee * - 12 days from your preferred dates.', NULL),
(131, 'Kashmir Tour Packages', 'Glimpse of Srinagar and Gulmarg with FREE Shikara Ride', 'admin@joy.com', '1', '1746614133.jpg', '<p><strong>Immerse yourself in the breathtaking beauty of Kashmir with our specially curated 3 Nights 4 Days tour. Explore the vibrant charm of Srinagar, with its serene Dal Lake, historic Mughal gardens, and rich cultural heritage. Then, escape to the enchanting meadows of Gulmarg, where snow-covered peaks, lush landscapes, and thrilling Gondola rides await. Whether you\'re seeking relaxation, adventure, or romance, this journey through paradise promises unforgettable moments and picture-perfect memories.</strong></p>', '4', '3', 'DAY 01: Arrival in Srinagar | Transfer to Gulmarg | Gulmarg Sightseeing Tour.,Welcome to Srinagar! Upon arrival at the airport,get transferred to Gulmarg. Post check-in,get driven to the Gulmarg Union Cab Stand. From there,you can walk or take a cab to the Gondola cable car station & ascend in the gondola (tickets not included),soaking in the panoramic views of the surrounding mountains and valleys. Also,you can visit the stunning Drung Waterfall or admire the Strawberry Valley before returning to the Gulmarg Union Cab Stand. From there,get driven to your hotel.,DAY 02: Transfer to Srinagar | Day at Leisure.,Today,after checking out,enjoy a scenic transfer to Srinagar. Upon arrival,check in at your hotel and spend the rest of your day at leisure,where you can explore the city on your own. You can visit Hari Parbat,a hilltop fortress,& soak-in the stunning views of the city. Also,you can admire the Indo-Saracenic architecture of the Jamia Masjid or you can try the famous Kahwa,a traditional Kashmiri green tea infused with spices and nuts. Afterwards,return to your hotel on your own.,DAY 03: Srinagar Sightseeing Tour | Shikara Ride and Houseboat Stay on Dal Lake.,Post check-out,enjoy a sightseeing tour of Srinagar. Begin by exploring the Mughal Gardens,like the Nishat Bagh,and soak-in the views of Dal Lake. Next,admire the Persian-style terraces of Shalimar Bagh & marvel at the Mughal architecture of the Pari Mahal. Then,pay your respects at the Shankaracharya Temple & enjoy the panoramic view of the city with Dal Lake from the temple. Later,enjoy a traditional Shikara ride on the Dal Lake before checking in to your houseboat for an overnight stay.,DAY 04: Departure Day.,check-out from your houseboat and get transferred to the Srinagar Airport for your journey back home! This marks the end to your amazing Kashmir trip!', 'Srinagar International Airport', 'Srinagar International Airport', '16999', NULL, '\"Lost in the beauty of Kashmir, found peace in my soul.\"', '11999', '9906786356', '2025-05-07 10:35:33', '2025-05-07 10:35:33', '1N Gulmarg', '1N Srinagar', '1N Dal Lake', 'Accommodation at hotel\r\nWelcome drink on arrival\r\nDaily breakfast and dinner\r\nNon A/C Vehicle for sightseeing\r\nAirport/Train Station Transfer\r\nAll applicable taxes', '5 % GST\r\nEntry fees to monuments and Palaces\r\nAny meals not mentioned, Any transfers, Any insurance\r\nAnything not mentioned in the inclusions', 'Travel Validity\r\nThe date is valid for travel till Tuesday, 30 September 2025.\r\n\r\nEasy Cancellation Policy\r\nIn case of more than 30 days prior to departure date, initial booking amount and any additional amount of air fare will be charged as penalty. *Less than 30 days: 50% of total tour cost will be charged as penalty.\r\n\r\nGuaranteed Dates\r\nYour selected travel dates are guaranteed in the unlikely event of a death and not due guarantee * - 12 days from your preferred dates.', NULL),
