(134, 'Ladakh Tour Packages', 'Breathtaking Leh with Khardung La Pass Visit', 'admin@joy.com', '1', '1746614798.jpg', '<p>Average elevation of the Ladakh region is around 3000 mts/ 10,000 ft. But&nbsp;<strong>it is home to some of the highest mountain passes in India, and the world</strong>. In fact, Ladakh boasts of the highest motorable mountain pass at 19,024 ft (5799 mts)&ndash; the Umling La pass.</p>', '04', '03', 'Arrival in Leh,Sham Valley,Magnetic Hill,Gurudwara Pathar Sahib,Hall of Fame,Spituk Monastery,Shanti Stupa,Leh Palace,Khardung La Pass Situated at an altitude of 18,379 feet,Khardung La is counted amongst the highest motorable passes in the world. Gateway to the remote Nubra and Shyok valleys,the mountain pass holds a strategic significance as supplies to the Siachen Glacier. Khardung La offers astonishing views and remains popular amongst travelers,especially adventure enthusiasts. Necessary precaution needs to be taken by all the travelers in general and people with breathing problems in particular,Departure from Leh', 'Leh Airport', 'Leh Airport', '25000', NULL, 'ROMANCE WITH LADAKH', '22000', '9906786356', '2025-05-07 10:46:38', '2025-05-07 10:46:38', 'leh', 'sham valley', 'Khardungla', 'Accommodation at hotel\r\nWelcome drink on arrival\r\nDaily breakfast and dinner\r\nNon A/C Vehicle for sightseeing\r\nAirport/Train Station Transfer\r\nAll applicable taxes', '5 % GST\r\nEntry fees to monuments and Palaces\r\nAny meals not mentioned, Any transfers, Any insurance\r\nAnything not mentioned in the inclusions', 'Travel Validity\r\nThe date is valid for travel till Tuesday, 30 September 2025.\r\n\r\nEasy Cancellation Policy\r\nIn case of more than 30 days prior to departure date, initial booking amount and any additional amount of air fare will be charged as penalty. *Less than 30 days: 50% of total tour cost will be charged as penalty.\r\n\r\nGuaranteed Dates\r\nYour selected travel dates are guaranteed in the unlikely event of a death and not due 