(135, 'Kashmir Tour Packages', 'Captivating Kashmir | Journey to Heaven', 'admin@joy.com', '1', '1746614803.jpg', '<h2 class=\"MicroComponents_curtomHighlightHeader__n6HpR undefined \r\n            \"><span class=\"  \">Trip Highlights</span></h2>\r\n<ul class=\"MicroComponents_customHighlights__fDWhp\">\r\n<li>\r\n<div class=\" MicroComponents_customHighligtsPoint__4owW3\">\r\n<p>Relax by Srinagar&rsquo;s iconic Dal Lake, unwind in Pahalgam&rsquo;s lush meadows, and embrace Gulmarg&rsquo;s alpine charm, offering a peaceful escape into nature.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<div class=\" MicroComponents_customHighligtsPoint__4owW3\">\r\n<p>Explore Srinagar&rsquo;s Mughal gardens, Shalimar Bagh, Nishat Bagh, and Chashme Shahi &ndash;&nbsp;each showcasing beautiful floral arrangements, cascading fountains, and intricate architecture.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<div class=\" MicroComponents_customHighligtsPoint__4owW3\">\r\n<p>Soak in the Pahalgam&rsquo;s breathtaking views, with snow-capped mountains framing lush valleys like the Aru Valley, Betaab Valley, and Chandanwari.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<div class=\" MicroComponents_customHighligtsPoint__4owW3\">\r\n<p>Experience the beauty of nature as you glide gently on the calm waters of Dal Lake on a shikara ride in Srinagar, leaving behind the noise and bustle of the city.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<div class=\" MicroComponents_customHighligtsPoint__4owW3\">\r\n<p>Ascend the Apharwat Peak as you ride the famous Gulmarg Gondola, and witness an unparalleled panorama of the Himalayan range.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>', '5', '4', 'DAY 1 Arrival in Srinagar | Srinagar Sightseeing Tour Welcome to Srinagar! Upon arrival at the airport- get transferred to your hotel. Check in and relax for a while. Then- get transferred for a sightseeing tour of the city. Begin with a visit to the ancient Shankaracharya Temple- followed by the historic Pari Mahal. Continue your tour at the Mughal gardens‚ÄîShalimar Bagh- Nishat Bagh- and Chashmashahi‚Äîwhere you can admire the vibrant flora. Later- get transferred to your hotel for an overnight stay.,DAY 2 Transfer to Pahalgam | Pahalgam Sightseeing Tour Today- you\'ll be driven to Pahalgam- a beautiful town known as the \'Valley of Shepherds\'. Upon arrival- check in and relax for a while. Later- get driven to the Pahalgam Union Cab Stand- and from there- take a cab (at additional cost) to explore Aru Valley- Betaab Valley- named after the Bollywood movie \'Betaab\' & visit Chandanwari- where snow-clad mountains create beautiful scenery. You can enjoy rafting at the Lidder River. Later- head to Union Cab Stand and get driven to your hotel.,DAY 3 Transfer to Gulmarg | Day at Leisure In the morning- check out of your hotel and get transferred to Gulmarg. Then get driven along the Lidder River- which offers stunning views of the surrounding hills. Upon arrival- check in and relax for a while. You can visit the Seven Springs- celebrated for its natural beauty. Then- explore the Shrine of Baba Reshi- a significant pilgrimage site. You can discover the Maharani Temple- known for its beautiful carvings and peaceful atmosphere. Later- return to your hotel for an overnight stay.,DAY 4 Gulmarg Sightseeing Tour | Transfer to Srinagar | Houseboat Stay Experience Check out of the hotel and board your transfer to the Gulmarg Union Cab Stand. Take a cab (at additional cost) and visit the Drung Waterfall and Strawberry Valley. You may also treat yourself to lunch at Igloo Cafe and enjoy the famous Gulmarg Gondola (at your own cost) to ascend the Apharwat Peak for panoramic views of the Himalayas. Later- head back to the cab stand on your own- from there you will get transferred to the Dal Lake in Srinagar. Board your houseboat for an overnight stay.,DAY 5 Departure Day In the morning check out of your hotel and get transferred to Srinagar Airport/Railway Station for an onward journey back home. This marks the end of your trip.', 'Srinagar International Airport', 'Srinagar International Airport', '19999', NULL, 'Paradise on Earth', '15999', '9906786356', '2025-05-07 10:46:43', '2025-05-07 10:46:43', '2N Srinagar', '1N Gulmarg', '1N Pahalgam', 'Accommodation at hotel\r\nWelcome drink on arrival\r\nDaily breakfast and dinner\r\nNon A/C Vehicle for sightseeing\r\nAirport/Train Station Transfer\r\nAll applicable taxes', '5 % GST\r\nEntry fees to monuments and Palaces\r\nAny meals not mentioned, Any transfers, Any insurance\r\nAnything not mentioned in the inclusions', 'Travel Validity\r\nThe date is valid for travel till Tuesday, 30 September 2025.\r\n\r\nEasy Cancellation Policy\r\nIn case of more than 30 days prior to departure date, initial booking amount and any additional amount of air fare will be charged as penalty. *Less than 30 days: 50% of total tour cost will be charged as penalty.\r\n\r\nGuaranteed Dates\r\nYour selected travel dates are guaranteed in the unlikely event of a death and not due guarantee * - 12 days from your preferred dates.', NULL);
