(147, 'Kashmir Tour Packages', 'Joy Jewels of Kashmir', 'admin@joy.com', '1', '1746687458.jpg', '<p>Escape to the serene beauty of Kashmir with our specially curated 5-day tour package. Witness snow-capped mountains, shimmering lakes, colorful gardens, and experience the warm hospitality of the Kashmiri people. Ideal for couples, families, and nature lovers!</p>', '05', '04', 'Day 1: on our arrival; at srinagar airport you will be warmly welcomed by our representative and directly proceed to srinagar hotel later explore mughal gardens like Nighat garden Shalimar garden Pari Mahal Chashmashi and Shankar Acharya Temple. Later return back to hotel for dinner and over night stay at Srinagar city.,Day 2: Day trip to Sonmarg: After breakfast drive towards Sonmarg. Visit Thajwas Glacier by hiring ponies. Explore Zero point ( Gateway of Ladakh) is a high altitude beautiful spot located 25 Km away from Sonmarg. It is Known for its eye catching views snow covered peaks and lush green meadows. later return back to srinagar for dinner and overnight stay at srinagar city,Day 3: Day trip to Gulmarg: After breakfast drive towards Gulmarg. Enjoy the Gulmarg Gondola Ride which is asias largest cable car ride. Explore the gulmarg golf cource and visit Alpather Lake. If time allows you can visit the Maharani Temple or Strawberry Valley. Latre return back to Srinagar for dinner and over night stay in Hotel.,Day 4: Day trip to Pahalgam: After breakfast you will directly proceed towards Pahalgam Valley. Explore Aru valley Betaab Valley and Chandanwari by hiring union cabs. You can visit Baisaran Valle by horses. Later return back to srinagar for dinner and overnight stay in Houseboat in Dal Lake.,Day 5: Departure: After breakfast transfer to Srinagar Airport to connect onward journey with great memories of Joy Tour and travels', 'Srinagar International Airport', 'Srinagar International Airport', '36000', NULL, 'Free Gondola Ist Phase', '32000', '9906786356', '2025-05-07 11:15:14', '2025-