(229, 'Ladakh Tour Packages', 'Best of Ladakh ‚Äì 6 Nights / 7 Days Tour Package', 'admin@joy.com', '1', '1748417757.jpg', '<p>This 7 day trip through high mountain passes, glistening lakes, historic monasteries, and isolated valleys will allow you to fully appreciate Ladakh\'s natural beauty and cultural diversity.<br>The charming Nubra Valley, the famous Pangong Lake, and the historic town of Leh are all included in this thoughtfully planned itinerary. Marvel at the tranquility of monasteries like Hemis and Thiksey, experience the exhilaration of traversing Khardung La, one of the highest motorable roads in the world, and take in Pangong Tso\'s shifting colors. This tour provides the ideal mix of adventure, leisure, and spiritual exploration with its carefully thought-out acclimatization, cozy accommodations, and picturesque drives.</p>\r\n<p>This trip promises to be filled with unforgettable experiences, whether you\'re an adventurer, nature lover, or someone just wanting to relax in the Himalayas.</p>', '7', '6', 'Turtuk,Khardung La Pass,Chang La Pass,Historic Monastries', 'Kushok Bakula Rimpochee ( Leh Airport)', 'Accommodation at hotel\r\nWelcome drink on arrival\r\nDaily breakfast and dinner\r\nNon A/C Vehicle for sightseeing\r\nAirport/Train Station Transfer\r\nAll applicable taxes', '40000', NULL, 'Including Inner Line Permit', '45000', '9906786356', '2025-05-28 07:35:57', '2025-05-28 07:35:57', '3N Leh', '2N Nubra', '1N Pangong', NULL, '5 % GST\r\nEntry fees to monuments and Palaces\r\nAny meals not mentioned, Any transfers, Any insurance\r\nAnything not mentioned in the inclusions', 'Standard check-in time at the hotel is normally 2:00 pm and check-out is 11:00 am. An early checkin, or a late checkout is solely based on the discretion of the hotel.\r\n\r\nPlease note that AC will be switched off during up-hill drives and at certain other times if you have\r\nopted for the ac vehcle. This will be completely dependent on the driver‚Äôs discretion.\r\n\r\nT