rect payment basis. In case of a\r\nhouseboat stay, an extra amount will be charged for Bukhari (traditional heater) for which the\r\npayment must be made directly at the location. Please note that room heaters in hotels and\r\nhouseboats will be available for a fixed time only.\r\n\r\nDuring peak winters, hot water supply at the hotel may be limited or time bound.\r\n\r\nAccommodation in the quaint houseboats of Kashmir is purely for the experience. Unlike hotels,\r\nhouseboats are faced with certain limitations such as lack of transportation between the houseboat\r\nand land, limited food menu, intermittent power supply and water supply, etc.\r\n\r\nIn Gulmarg, the horseman union does not allow any vehicle to drop or pick up guests at/from the\r\ngondola. All sightseeing tours are also prohibited by the union.\r\n\r\nAru Valley, Chandanwari and Betaab Valley at Pahalgam are not part of the itinerary (unless\r\nincluded) due to restrictions by the local transport union.\r\n\r\nYou have an hour each to enjoy the picturesque snow-clad mountains and the green valleys of Aru\r\nValley, Betab Valley and Chandanwari in Pahalgam. If you wish to spend more time exploring these\r\nareas, you would have to pay the applicable additional amount to the driver/taxi union.\r\n\r\nOnly vehicles allotted by the Local Unions of Pahalgam and Sonmarg can be used for sightseeing in\r\nthe regions, and may not be as per the usual standards of Joy Tour and Travels.\r\n\r\nDuring winter, the road to Sonmarg remains closed and vehicles can only go up to Gagangir.\r\nFor Sonmarg sightseeing, our vehicle will take the guest to the Sonmarg taxi stand. From there, the\r\nguest needs to hire a pony/local union cab for sightseeing. Thajwas Glacier, Zero Point at Sonmarg\r\nare not included in the tour, due to restrictions laid down by the local union.\r\n\r\nDue to a ban on new construction in Gulmarg, Pahalgam, and a few areas of Srinagar such as Dal\r\nLake and Boulevard Road, some hotels may appear to be in a dilapidated state. Rest assured, these\r\nhotels provide excellent facilities and hospitality.\r\n\r\nIn case of road closure due to snow and slippery roads, our vehicle will not be allowed to ply as a\r\nprecautionary measure. This is as per govt./administration orders. Only snow jeeps/chained vehicles\r\nare allowed to ply. These vehicles can be hired on a direct payment basis or the same can be arranged\r\nby us at an additional cost.\r\n\r\nThe package price doesn‚Äôt include special dinner or mandatory charges at time levied by the hotels\r\nespecially during New Year and Christmas or any special occasions. Joy Tour and Travels shall try to\r\ncommunicate the same while booking the package. However Joy Tour and Travels may not have this\r\ninformation readily available all the time.\r\n\r\nIn case your package needs to be cancelled due to any natural calamity, weather conditions etc. Joy\r\nTour and Travels shall strive to give you the maximum possible refund subject to the agreement\r\nmade with our trade partners/vendors.\r\n\r\nJoy Tour and Travels reserves the right to modify the itinerary at any point, due to reasons including\r\nbut not limited to: Force Majeure events, strikes, fairs, festivals, weather conditions, traffic problems,\r\noverbooking of hotels / flights, cancellation / rerouting of flights, closure of /entry restrictions at a\r\nplace of visit, etc. While we will do our best to make suitable alternate arrangements, we would not\r\nbe held liable for any refunds/compensation claims arising out of this. Moreover, any additional cost\r\ninvolved due to Force Majeure cases will have to be borne by guest.\r\n\r\nRefund policy in case guest cancels or postpones due to any reason. If company finds a genuine\r\nreason after proper investigation will issue a credit note as per the company policy, that credit note can be utilized for upcoming tour valid for one year from the date of issuance.\r\n\r\nIf You Have A Complaint:\r\n\r\n\r\nWe aim to provide the best tour package possible based on your preference. However, if you are not satisfied please complain as soon as possible to the relevant person or representative and we will do everything reasonably possible to sort the problem out. If you are still not satisfied, If you do not have the services of a Representative, you must contact us at the given Email ID or Phone Number during the tour. No complaints or refund requests for the same be entertained after the tour ends.\r\n\r\nPlease Note:\r\nServices such as Shikara rides, union taxis, the Gulmarg Gondola, local shopping experiences, and pony rides are operated by independent providers and are not directly managed or controlled by our travel agency. While we are happy to assist with information or guidance regarding these services, we cannot be held responsible for any issues, delays, or disputes that may arise from their use.', NULL);
INSERT INTO `package_days` (`id`, `day_index`, `package_id`, `days`, `title`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(117, 1, 203, 'Local Sightseeing', 'Srinagar Airport', '2025-05-13 09:25:33', '2025-05-13 09:25:33'),
(118, 2, 203, 'Gulmarg', 'Gulmarg Day Trip', '2025-05-13 09:25:33', '2025-05-13 09:25:33'),
(119, 3, 203, 'Srinagar International Airport', 'Airport Drop', '2025-05-13 09:25:33', '2025-05-13 09:25:33'),
(121, 1, 204, 'On arrival at the Srinagar Airport, you will be welcomed by the agent‚Äôs representative- who will then transfer you to a jetty around the Dal Lake. The houseboats in Dal Lake are docked at the jetty. After check-in and lunch in the houseboat- you can relax for a while.\r\nLater in the evening- you will be taken for a Shikara ride to the Nehru Park. The day concludes with dinner in the houseboat. Night halt at the houseboat. Distance from Srinagar Airport to Dal Lake: 24 km', 'Srinagar: Pick up from Airport, Transfer to the Houseboat', '2025-05-15 05:43:27', '2025-05-15 05:43:27'),
(122, 2, 204, 'After a filling breakfast, you will be transferred to Gulmarg. The day is available for leisure activities such as golf, nature walks, bird watching, and pony rides. But the most exciting activity that you must not miss is the famous Gondola ride that takes you towards Apharwat via Kongdori. Your Kashmir holiday package includes lunch and dinner served in the Gulmarg hotel. Enjoy the night stay at the Gulmarg hotel. Distance from Dal Lake to Gulmarg: 56 km', 'Srinagar to Gulmarg: Getaway to Gulmarg', '2025-05-15 05:43:27', '2025-05-15 05:43:27'),
(123, 3, 204, 'Have breakfast in the hotel at Gulmarg, after which you will be transferred to Pahalgam. You can see the saffron fields and visit the Anantnag Sulpher Springs en route. You can have lunch at a local restaurant. The rest of the day is offered to you for leisure activities. You can visit the Amusement Park by the Lidder River or go for white river rafting in the Aru Valley. Pony rides are also available to Baisaran, Betaab Valley, and Chandanwari. Overnight stay in Hotel at Pahalgam Valley.', 'Gulmarg to Pahalgam: Valley of Shephards', '2025-05-15 05:43:27', '2025-05-15 05:43:27'),
(124, 4, 204, 'After breakfast in your hotel at Pahalgam you will be transferred to the Srinagar Airport. The transfer is included in the tour package for Kashmir. This concludes your holiday in Kashmir.', 'Srinagar: Departure from Srinagar', '2025-05-15 05:43:27', '2025-05-15 05:43:27'),
(125, 1, 205, 'Begin your Kashmir sightseeing with the enchanting town of Pahalgam.\r\nArrive at the airport in Jammu As your Kashmir package begins, an agent‚Äôs representative will receive and escort you to your hotel in Pahalgam. Take in the breathtaking and awe-inspiring scenery enroute as your romance in this paradise blooms.\r\nComplete the check-in formalities once you reach the hotel and enjoy a warm Kashmiri dinner.', 'Pahalgam: Arrival to the paradise on earth', '2025-05-15 06:24:49', '2025-05-15 06:24:49'),
(126, 2, 205, 'Wake up amidst picturesque meadows and lush greenery on the second day of your Kashmir package.\r\n\r\nAfter a healthy breakfast, gear up for local sightseeing in Pahalgam. You can visit the Jama Masjid Mosque, the Gauri Shankar Temple, or stop by at the serene Aru Valley and Betaab Valley. White water rafting in Lidder river is also extremely popular among couples.\r\n\r\nLater as part of your Kashmir sightseeing, proceed to Srinagar for a scintillating houseboat stay which also includes a shikara ride and a romantic candle light dinner and cake. Offering a serene environment and amorous setting, the houseboat will truly enchant you and your partner.', 'Srinagar: Sightseeing and Houseboat stay', '2025-05-15 06:24:49', '2025-05-15 06:24:49'),
(127, 3, 205, 'Gear up to revel amidst snow covered peaks on the third day of your Kashmir trip.\r\nAfter a healthy Kashmiri breakfast in the houseboat, complete the check-out formalities and proceed to the picturesque town of Gulmarg.\r\nYour day is at leisure and you can proceed for Kashmir sightseeing on your own. Explore the scenic beauty of Gulmarg with your better half today. Head to the Strawberry Field where the popular Shah Rukh Khan starrer Jab Tak Hai Jaan was shot or take an excursion to the Alpather Lake.\r\nCome back to the hotel for a delicious Kashmiri dinner and later, snuggle the night away.', 'Gulmarg: Arrival and leisure day', '2025-05-15 06:24:49', '2025-05-15 06:24:49'),
(128, 4, 205, 'Visit the delightful town of Gulmarg today which is among the primary Kashmir honeymoon places.\r\nAfter a delectable breakfast served in hotel, head out to enjoy a romantic day in the Gulmarg valley on your Kashmir trip. You can visit the Maharani temple, Ziarat of Baba Reshi, and the Gulmarg golf course.\r\nLater, head for the famous Gondola cable car ride or pony ride with your beloved and take in the mesmerizing panorama. You can also go on nature walks or short hikes.\r\nCome back to the hotel for a cozy dinner and overnight stay', 'Gulmarg: Sightseeing tour', '2025-05-15 06:24:49', '2025-05-15 06:24:49'),
(129, 5, 205, 'On the penultimate day of your Kashmir trip, visit the capital city of Srinagar.\r\nAfter a delicious breakfast, check-out from your hotel in Gulmarg and proceed to the capital city of Srinagar. You can take an excursion directly to the divine Shankaracharya Hill Temple. After which, proceed for hotel check-in and complete the registration formalities.\r\nIn the evening, visit the grand Mughal Gardens - the Shalimar Bagh, Nishat Bagh, Pari Mahal and Chasmashahi to spend quality time with your spouse amidst heritage and charming gardens, the most popular Kashmir honeymoon places.\r\nCome back to the hotel for a dinner and prepare for your journey back home.', 'Srinagar: Arrival and sightseeing tour', '2025-05-15 06:24:49', '2025-05-15 06:24:49'),
(130, 6, 205, 'Your 5 nights 6 days Trip in Kashmir ends as you get ready for the journey back home.', 'Srinagar: Departure', '2025-05-15 06:24:49', '2025-05-15 06:24:49'),
(134, 1, 206, 'Welcome to Srinagar, the summer capital of Jammu and Kashmir!\r\nYour exploration in Kashmir starts with your arrival at the Srinagar airport. On arrival, meet our travel representative and proceed towards the hotel in Srinagar. Check-in at the hotel and freshen up. Visit all the beautifully landscaped, lush green Mughals gardens of Srinagar including Shalimar Bagh, Nishat Bagh and Cheshmashahi and stroll around enjoying these architectural marvels majestically depicting Islamic architecture. After this, pay a visit to the famous Shankaracharya Temple, a Hindu place of worship dedicated to Lord Shiva. Later in the evening, enjoy the Shikara ride on the Dal Lake and spend the night at the cozy houseboat after a heavenly dinner.', 'Srinagar: Arrival and Sightseeing', '2025-05-15 06:36:22', '2025-05-15 06:36:22'),
(135, 2, 206, 'Enjoy the day at India‚Äôs best skiing destination!\r\nHave breakfast and head towards Gulmarg. Enjoy a lush breakfast and head to Gulmarg, one of the best skiing destinations in the world. Here, visit the golf course at an altitude of 2730 meters above mean sea level. You can also enjoy the gondola ride (cable car ride) up to Khilanmarg at your personal expense and enjoy strikingly beautiful panoramic views of the Himalayan ranges drapes in layers of snow. Later in the evening, return to Srinagar. Have a scrumptious dinner at the hotel and catch up a sound sleep in the warm room of the hotel.', 'Srinagar: Gulmarg Tour', '2025-05-15 06:36:22', '2025-05-15 06:36:22'),
(136, 3, 206, 'Relish the beauty of Sonmarg, the meadow of gold!\r\nKick start the day with a healthy breakfast and get ready for the excursion trip to Sonmarg. Sonmarg is abundantly blessed with pristine lakes, mighty glaciers, alluring passes and picturesque rivers. The carpet of golden yellow alpine flowers is indeed a visual delight here. Visit all the major places of attractions here and get back to the hotel in Srinagar for a delectable dinner and comfortable overnight stay.', 'Srinagar: Sonmarg Sightseeing', '2025-05-15 06:36:22', '2025-05-15 06:36:22'),
(137, 4, 206, 'Enjoy sightseeing in Pahalgam, the valley of the shepherds!\r\nSavor a delicious breakfast at the hotel in Srinagar. Then, proceed towards Pahalgam for sightseeing. Pahalgam is a peaceful town perfect beautifully on the banks of River Lidder. Visit the sprawling Betaab Valley, a perfect camping site for explorers. As a part of the itinerary, you can then proceed for sightseeing to Chandanwari glacier point and Aru valley by local taxi and enjoy the mesmerizing beauty around. In the evening, get back to the hotel in Srinagar. Enjoy pleasant conversations with your family over a luscious dinner on this penultimate day and wind off the day with a peaceful sleep.', 'Sringar: Pahalgam Sightseeing', '2025-05-15 06:36:22', '2025-05-15 06:36:22'),
(138, 5, 206, 'Enjoy a tasty breakfast and check-out from the hotel. Proceed towards the airport and embark your homebound journey with an extra backpack of colorful and happy memories from this Kashmir trip.', 'Srinagar: Departure', '2025-05-15 06:36:22', '2025-05-15 06:36:22'),
(583, 1, 182, 'Srinagar local sightseeing visit Nishat Garden, Shalimar Garden, Pari Mahal, Chashmashahi, Shankaracharya Temple', 'Arrival and local sightseeing of Srinagar', '2025-05-20 10:10:56', '2025-05-20 10:10:56'),
(584, 2, 182, 'Srinagar City to Gulmarg Valley visiting Apple Gardens, Tangmarg Valley, Drung Waterfall with union Taxi, Gulmarg Valley. Also Explore Gondola Rides both Phases Kongdor and Affarwat. Overnight Stay in Hotel at Gulmarg Valley', 'Srinagar City---Gulmarg Valley', '2025-05-20 10:10:56', '2025-05-20 10:10:56'),
(585, 3, 182, 'Explore Gulmarg local market and Snow activities like snow boarding skiing skating and other snow sport activities', 'Gulmarg Local sightseeing', '2025-05-20 10:10:56', '2025-05-20 10:10:56'),
(586, 4, 182, 'After breakfast, And Transfer to Srinagar Airport to connect onward journey with great memories of Joy Tour and Travels.', 'Drop at Srinagar City', '2025-05-20 10:10:56', '2025-05-20 10:10:56'),
(595, 1, 132, 'on your arrival at Srinagar Airport you will be warmly welcomed and transfer towards srinagar hotel, later explore mughal gardens like Nishat Garden, Shalimar Garden, Pari Mahal, Chashmashahi & Shankaracharya Temple. Later return back to hotel for dinner and overnight stay in Srinagar City.', 'Arrival and local sightseeing of Srinagar', '2025-05-21 05:39:28', '2025-05-21 05:39:28'),
(596, 2, 132, 'After breakfast from Srinagar hotel later drive towards Sonmarg Meadow of Gold. Visit Mamar Valley, Gagangir Valley, Lovers Point on the way. Visit zero point by hiring union cabs. Explore Thajiwas Glacier by hiring ponies. Later drive towards srinagar for dinner and overnight stay in Hotel.', 'Day trip to Sonmarg', '2025-05-21 05:39:28', '2025-05-21 05:39:28'),
(597, 3, 132, 'After breakfast from Srinagar hotel later drive towards Gulmarg Meadow of Flowers. Explore Gondola Ride worlds largest asia`s cable car ride. Explore local places and parks of Gulmarg, later return back towards srinagar for dinner and overnight stay in Hotel.', 'Day trip to Gulmarg', '2025-05-21 05:39:28', '2025-05-21 05:39:28'),
(598, 4, 132, 'After breakfast from Srinagar Hotel later you will proceed towards Pahalgam valley of Shepherds. Visit Saffron Fields, Bat Factory, Awantipora Ruins, Aabshar Point, Rafting Point on the way. Later explore Aru Valley Betaab Valley and Chandanwari b hiring union cabs. Later return to srinagar for dinner and overnight stay in Houseboat in Dal Lake.', 'Day trip to Pahalgam', '2025-05-21 05:39:28', '2025-05-21 05:39:28'),
(599, 5, 132, 'After Breakfast drive towards Srinagar Airport to connect onwards journey with unforgettable memories of joy tour & travels.', 'Departure', '2025-05-21 05:39:28', '2025-05-21 05:39:28'),
(600, 1, 184, 'On your arrival at Srinagar Airport you will be warmly welcomed by our representative and smooth transfer towards Srinagar, After reaching srinagar hotel complete all check in formalities at hotel, later explore Mughal Gardens like Nishat Garden, Shalimar Garden, Pari Mahal, Chashmashahi and Shankaracharya Temple. Later return back to hotel for dinner and overnight stay in srinagar city.', 'Arrival and local sightseeing of Srinagar', '2025-05-21 06:33:59', '2025-05-21 06:33:59'),
(601, 2, 184, 'After breakfast later drive towards Sonmarg Meadow of Gold. Visit Mamar Valley, Gagangir Valley, Lovers Point on the way. Explore zero point gate way of ladakh on your own cost. Visit Thajiwas Glacier by hiring ponies. Later return towards srinagar hotel for dinner and overnight stay.', 'Day trip to Sonmarg', '2025-05-21 06:33:59', '2025-05-21 06:33:59'),
(602, 3, 184, 'After breakfast you will proceed towards Gulmarg Meadow of Flowers. Explore Gondola Ride, world`s largest cable car ride. Explore Gulmarg local places and parks later drive back towards srinagar hotel for dinner and overnight stay in Srinagar city.', 'Day Trip to Gulmarg', '2025-05-21 06:33:59', '2025-05-21 06:33:59'),
(603, 4, 184, 'After breakfast drive towards Pahalgam Valley of Shepherds. Explore Saffron Fields, Awantipore Ruins, Bat Factory, Aabshar point, rafting Point on the way. Visit Aru Valley Betaab Valley and Chandanwari on you own cost. After full day enjoyment later drive towards Srinagar hotel for dinner and overnight stay in Srinagar City', 'Day Trip to Pahalgam', '2025-05-21 06:33:59', '2025-05-21 06:33:59'),
(604, 5, 184, 'After breakfast, start your day early and head to Doodhpathri, which is located about 42 km from Srinagar. Once you reach Doodhpathri, take a stroll around the lush green meadows and enjoy the scenic beauty of the place. The name Doodhpathri means \"Valley of Milk\" and it is known for its rolling hills, meadows, and gushing streams.You can also go for a horse ride or a trek to explore the nearby areas. The trek to the highest point of Doodhpathri, known as Tatta Kutti, is a must-do activity for adventure enthusiasts. Later rturn back to Srinagar for dinner and overnight stay in Houseboat in Dal Lake.', 'Day Trip to Dodhpathri', '2025-05-21 06:33:59', '2025-05-21 06:33:59'),
(605, 6, 184, 'After breakfast drive towards Srinagar Airport to connect onwards journey with unforgettable memories of Joy tour and travels.', 'Depauture', '2025-05-21 06:33:59', '2025-05-21 06:33:59'),
(606, 1, 175, 'On your arrival at Srinagar Airport you will be warmly welcomed and smooth transfer towards Srinagar, after reaching srinagar complete all check in formalities at Hotel, Later explore Mughal Gardens like Nishat Garden, Shalimar Garden, Pari Mahal, Chashmashahi, Shankar Acharya Temple. Later at evening return back towards Hotel for dinner and overnight stay in srinagar city.', 'Arrival and local sightseeing of Srinagar', '2025-05-21 07:03:42', '2025-05-21 07:03:42'),
(607, 2, 175, 'After breakfast from srinagar hotel you will proceed towards Sonmarg Meadow of Gold, explore Mamar valley, Gagangir Valley, Lovers Point on the way. Visit Zero point Gate Way of Ladakh on your own cost. Visit Thajiwas Glacier by hiring ponies. Later return back to srinagar for dinner and overnight stay in Srinagar City', 'Full Day Trip to Sonmarg', '2025-05-21 07:03:42', '2025-05-21 07:03:42'),
(608, 3, 175, 'After brekfast checkout from srinagar hotel, later drive towards Pahalgam Valley. Explore saffron fileds, Awantipora Ruins, Bat Factory, Aabshar Point, Rafting point. Visit Aru Valley Betaab Valley Chandanwari by union cabs. Later return towards Hotel for dinner and overnight stay in pahalgam Hotel.', 'Srinagar to Pahalgam Valley of Shepherds', '2025-05-21 07:03:42', '2025-05-21 07:03:42'),
(609, 4, 175, 'After breakfast from Pahalgam hotel later drive towards towards Gulmarg. After reaching Gulmarg complete all checkin formalities at hotel. Enjoy dinner and overnight stay in Gulmarg Valley.', 'Pahalgam to Gulmarg Meadow of Flowers', '2025-05-21 07:03:42', '2025-05-21 07:03:42'),
(610, 5, 175, 'After breakfast from Gulmarg hotel Later explore Gondola Ride which is Asia`s Largest cable car ride. After full day enjoyment later drive towards Srinagar for dinner and overnight stay in Houseboat in Dal Lake.', 'Gulmarg Local sightseeing to srinagar', '2025-05-21 07:03:42', '2025-05-21 07:03:42'),
(611, 6, 175, 'After breakfast drive towards Srinagar Airport to connect onwards journey with good memories of Joy travels.', 'Departure', '2025-05-21 07:03:42', '2025-05-21 07:03:42'),
(643, 1, 15, 'Arrival at Srinagar Airport and Srinagar Local Sightseeing Visit Nishat Bagh, Shalimar Bagh, Chashma Shahi Garden, Shankaracharya Temple  Boulevard Road and Dal Lake. Overnight stay in Hotel at Srinagar city.', 'Arrival Srinagar and local sightseeing', '2025-05-21 10:26:05', '2025-05-21 10:26:05'),
(644, 2, 15, 'Full Day Trip to Sonmarg Valley visit Mamar Valley, Gagangir, and Lovers Point. On arrival Visit Thajiwas Glacier with ponies and Zero point with Union Taxi. Overnight stay in Hotel at Srinagar City.', 'Full day trip to Sonmarg', '2025-05-21 10:26:05', '2025-05-21 10:26:05'),
(645, 3, 15, 'Full day trip to Gulmarg Valley visiting Apple Gardens, Tangmarg Valley, Drung Waterfall with Union Taxi, Gulmarg Valley. Also Explore Gondola Rides both Phases Kongdor and Affarwat. Overnight stay in a Hotel at Srinagar City.', 'Full Day trip to Gulmarg', '2025-05-21 10:26:05', '2025-05-21 10:26:05'),
(646, 4, 15, 'Dachigam National Park in Srinagar, Jammu and Kashmir, is primarily famous for the Kashmir stag, also known as the Hangul. It is the only area in India where this endangered deer species can be found. Additionally, the park is a significant wildlife destination, home to various other animals and bird species, including raptors and colorful pheasants. Overnight stay in Hotel at Srinagar City.', 'Full day trip to Dachigam', '2025-05-21 10:26:05', '2025-05-21 10:26:05'),
(647, 5, 15, 'Transfer to Pahalgam Valley on the way visit Saffron Filed, Awantipora Ruins, Bat Factory, Apple Garden, Rafting Point and Abshar Park. On arrival Visit Baisaran by Ponies. Overnight stay in Hotel at Pahalgam Valley.', 'Srinagar to Pahalgam', '2025-05-21 10:26:05', '2025-05-21 10:26:05'),
(648, 6, 15, 'Pahalgam valley local sightseeing visit Aru valley, Betaab valley and Chandanwari by Union Taxi.Overnight stay in Hotel at Pahalgam Valley.', 'Pahalgam Local Sightseeing', '2025-05-21 10:26:05', '2025-05-21 10:26:05'),
