(805, 1, 38, 'Embrace the spirit of Ladakh as you arrive ‚Äì welcome! After arriving at Leh airport, you will be transferred to your pre-booked hotel in Leh. Check in and rest for a while before embarking on a sightseeing tour of Leh. You will be visiting Leh Palace, Shanti Stupa, a peaceful Buddhist white domed stupa, and later continue your day tour with a visit to the vibrant Leh market. Afterwards, you\'ll head back to the hotel for an overnight stay. (Note: Vehicle will be provided as per group size.)', 'Arrival in Leh | Sightseeing Tour in Leh', '2025-05-22 10:22:38', '2025-05-22 10:22:38'),
(806, 2, 38, 'In the morning, you will be driven to Sham Valley. Begin your exploration at the Spituk Gompa and then the Sangam Point, a beautiful confluence of the Zanskar & Indus river. Next, make a stop at the Gurudwara Pathar Sahib, & drive through the mysterious Magnetic Hills. You will also visit the SECMOL School, before heading towards the famous Hall of Fame. Afterwards, you can enjoy a White Water Rafting before returning to your hotel in Leh for an overnight stay.', 'Day Trip to Sham Valley | Exploring the Ladakhi Culture', '2025-05-22 10:22:38', '2025-05-22 10:22:38'),
(807, 3, 38, 'After breakfast, you will embark on an exciting journey towards the world\'s highest all season motorable pass - Khardung La Pass. Enjoy the dramatic shift in scenery amidst the mighty Himalayan peak. During your excursion, make a stop at the famous Rinchen cafe for a steaming bowl of Maggi and a refreshing chai. Later, head back to Leh for overnight stay.', 'Day Trip Across Khardung-La Pass | Driving Across the Highest All Season Motorable Pass', '2025-05-22 10:22:38', '2025-05-22 10:22:38'),
(808, 4, 38, 'Begin your day trip to the breathtaking Pangong Tso, driving past the rugged terrains of Ladakh. After you arrive at the Pangong Tso, spend the time admiring the dreamy landscapes and the vibrant shades of the lake, changing from blue to turquoise. As you return to Leh via Chang La Pass, you will make stops at the Chang La Baba Temple, Thiksey Monastery and Druk Padma School. Afterwards, you will return to your hotel in Leh for a comfortable overnight stay.', 'Day Trip to Pangong Lake | En-route sightseeing from Pangong Tso to Leh', '2025-05-22 10:22:38', '2025-05-22 10:22:38'),
(809, 5, 38, 'After checking out of your hotel, you will be transferred to Leh airport. Take one last glance at the towering peaks, bid farewell to Ladakh, and board your flight back home, marking the end of your trip.', 'Departure Day', '2025-05-22 10:22:38', '2025-05-22 10:22:38'),
