(998, 1, 20, 'By the morning, your bus ride will come to a halt at the Manali Bus Stand. From there, get transferred to the hotel in Manali and check to freshen up. Later, board your pre-booked transfer for a sightseeing tour including a visit to popular sites such as the Hidimba Devi Temple, Vashist Kund, and Van Vihar National Park. Also, stop by to explore a Tibetan Monastery and have a shopping spree on the Mall Road. In the evening, get dropped off at the hotel for an overnight stay.', 'Arrival Manali', '2025-05-24 06:38:14', '2025-05-24 06:38:14'),
(999, 2, 20, 'Manali to Jispa | Experience the changing landscape as you enter Lahaul Valley', 'Manali to Jispa', '2025-05-24 06:38:14', '2025-05-24 06:38:14'),
(1000, 3, 20, 'Jispa to Leh | Drive Through Gata Loops, 21 Hairpin Bends', 'jispa to leh', '2025-05-24 06:38:14', '2025-05-24 06:38:14'),
(1001, 4, 20, 'Wake up to a beautiful morning in the mountains and have a hearty breakfast.\r\nGet ready for an adventurous drive to \'Sham Valley\', which is beautifully nestled around the Srinagar - Leh highway.\r\nStart off the sightseeing by paying homage to the martyrs of the Indo-Pak War at the Hall of Fame.\r\nVisit the Spituk Gompa which also has a museum on the premises housing ancient masks, weapons and Thangkas (Buddhist Paintings).\r\nEnjoy delicious langar at Gurudwara Pathar Sahib and know the story behind the construction of this Gurudwara by the army.\r\nAnother interesting place to visit today is Magnetic Hill, a small stretch of the road that defies the law of gravity.\r\nVisit Indus Sangam Viewpoint to watch the confluence of Zanskar and Indus Rivers.\r\nVisit SECMOL which is the real 3-idiots school.\r\nAfter a day filled with fun and adventure, return back to the hotel for dinner and an overnight stay in Leh.', 'Leh city sightseeing', '2025-05-24 06:38:14', '2025-05-24 06:38:14'),
(1002, 5, 20, 'Leh to Nubra Valley via Khardung-La Pass | A Drive to the World‚Äôs Highest Motorable Road (18000 ft.)', 'Leh to nubra', '2025-05-24 06:38:14', '2025-05-24 06:38:14'),
(1003, 6, 20, 'Nubra Valley to Pangong Lake | Recreate The Famous Bollywood Moments', 'Nubra to Pangong', '2025-05-24 06:38:14', '2025-05-24 06:38:14'),
(1004, 7, 20, 'Pangong Lake to Leh | Excursion to Rancho School', 'Pangong to leh', '2025-05-24 06:38:14', '2025-05-24 06:38:14'),
(1005, 8, 20, 'Visit Magnetic hill, Pathar Sahib Gurudwara, Indus Zaskar sangam followed by visit to Moon land.. Further drive to Alchi Gompa. It bears the name of Alchi from the language of pre-Tibetan Dardic inhabitants. The Alchi Chos-khor consists of unique paintings, which may be attributed from the mid to late 11th century and was constructed by the famous translator Rin-chen bzang po. The paintings are characterized according to the Tabo and Tholing. At the entrance gate, light stupas are constructed and are known as Kakini choten. Arrive in Kargil.', 'leh to kargil', '2025-05-24 06:38:14', '2025-05-24 06:38:14'),
