(1216, 4, 82, 'Leh Lamayuru Alchi Leh After breakfast proceed for Lamayuru Monastery (4-5 hrs drive). En route visit Patharsaheb Gurudwara confluence of Indus and Zanskar rivers Magnetic Hill. Explore Lamayuru Monastery & enjoy magnificent view of Moonland An undulating series of mountains that resemble the surface of the moon Later proceed for Alchi monastery mainly known for its magnificent and well-preserved 10th century wall paintings. Back to Leh by evening.Overnight Stay in a Hotel at Leh City.', 'Full Day Trip to Alchi Monastery.', '2025-05-27 06:31:45', '2025-05-27 06:31:45'),
