(1715, 1, 40, 'Juley! Welcome to the Land of High Passes. Upon reaching, get transferred to the hotel and freshen up. Then, get assisted for a sightseeing tour of Leh. First, visit the Leh Palace and dive deep into the royal heritage of the destination, followed by a visit to the Shanti Stupa where you can enjoy breathtaking views of the Leh cityscape and the surrounding mountains. At your last stop, immerse yourself in the vibrant ambience of Leh Marketplace before heading back to your hotel for the night.', 'Arrival in Leh | Behold the Beauty of Leh', '2025-06-02 11:04:48', '2025-06-02 11:04:48'),
(1716, 2, 40, 'Get ready to take a tour of the beautiful Sham Valley. Enjoy a scenic drive and visit the Sangam Point (meeting point of the Zanskar and Indus Rivers) and the Magnetic Hill. On this journey, you will also visit attractions such as Gurudwara Pathar Sahib, SECMOL Campus featured in the \"3 Idiots\" Bollywood film, and the Hall of Fame War Memorial. Wind up your day and return to the hotel in Leh for an overnight stay.', 'Leh to Sham Valley | Sham Valley Excursion', '2025-06-02 11:04:48', '2025-06-02 11:04:48'),
(1717, 3, 40, 'Check-out from Leh and begin your journey to Nubra Valley via Khardung La Pass (world‚Äôs highest all-season motorable pass). Ride past the ancient Diskit Monastery and witness the enormous Maitreya Buddha Statue. Then, reach the Hunder Sand Dunes where you can enjoy a double-humped camel ride or an ATV ride, exploring the cold deserts of Nubra Valley. Later, get assisted to the campsite by the Shyok River and watch the stars dazzle at night as you enjoy your overnight stay here.', 'Leh to Nubra via Khardung La Pass | Exploring the Cold Deserts of Nubra', '2025-06-02 11:04:48', '2025-06-02 11:04:48'),
(1718, 4, 40, 'For this day, get transferred to the Turtuk village from the Nubra Valley campsite. Admire beauty of this region which lies in the steep mountain slopes that surround the lush green village. Explore Turtuk on foot and experience the unique culture and traditions of the Balti people. Witness the vast Apricot and Apple Orchards, take a tour of the Turtuk Monastery, and then finally visit the enormous Turtuk Polo Ground. Later, get assisted back to your camp in Nubra Valley for an overnight stay.', 'Excursion to Turtuk Village | The Home of the Baltis', '2025-06-02 11:04:48', '2025-06-02 11:04:48'),
(1719, 5, 40, 'Wake up to another day of adventure on your Ladakh tour. Check-out from the Nubra Valley camp and start your trip by visiting Pangong Lake. Drive by the Shyok River while soaking-in the majestic beauty of the landscape. Reach and check-in to your stay, then witness the Pangong Lake and spend time by its quiet waters. Return to your camp for an overnight stay.', 'Trip from Nubra to Pangong | Camping at Pangong', '2025-06-02 11:04:48', '2025-06-02 11:04:48'),
(1720, 6, 40, 'As you travel from Pangong to Leh after checking-out from your stay, you will cross on of the highest motorable passes in the world, Chang La. Then, visit the Druk Padma Karpo School (Rancho School), featured in the Bollywood blockbuster film ‚Äò3 Idiots‚Äô. Continue to the Thiksey Monastery, the largest monastery in Central Ladakh where you can take-in the tranquil ambience of the place and enjoy the true essence of Ladakh. Later, get assisted to the hotel in Leh and check-in for an overnight stay.', 'Journey from Pangong to Leh | Rounding off the journey', '2025-06-02 11:04:48', '2025-06-02 11:04:48'),
