(1830, 1, 44, 'Welcome to Srinagar, the Venice of Kashmir. Upon your arrival, reach the pick-up point, Tourist Reception Center on your own to get transferred to the campsite in Sonamarg and check-in. You can relax at the campsite or explore the beautiful town of Sonmarg and see the amazing Thajiwas Glacier, Baltal Valley, and many more attractions. After an amazing day, head back to the campsite for an overnight stay.', 'Arrival at Srinagar International Airport and Transfer to Sonamarg Valley.', '2025-06-04 09:59:38', '2025-06-04 09:59:38'),
(1831, 2, 44, 'Have a beautiful beginning of the day as you wake up with a backdrop of lush greenery. After having breakfast, pack your bags and leave for Nichnai, the Valley of Wild Flowers. You will pass via Shekdur, where you can take a stopover to have maggie and tea. Continue the journey, and after reaching the Nichnai campsite, enjoy your overnight stay.', 'Trek from Sonamarg to Nichnai | A Walk Through The Meadows of Gold.', '2025-06-04 09:59:38', '2025-06-04 09:59:38'),
(1832, 3, 44, 'Get dressed up in your comfortable clothes to begin your trek towards Vishansar Lake. As you walk along the riverbank, enjoy a gradual ascent through the meadow that will take you to the Nichnai Pass, giving panoramic views of the Sonamarg valley. Continue your journey, which will soon lead you to Vishansar Lake, a breathtaking sight with towering mountains, and enjoy your overnight stay.', 'Trek from Nichnai to Vishansar Lake | Admire Views of Snowcapped Mountains.', '2025-06-04 09:59:38', '2025-06-04 09:59:38'),
(1833, 4, 44, 'After you pack up, embark on a trek to Krishansar Peak, located 500 ft. above the campsite. Then cross and reach the other side of the reservoir, where the path will lead you to Krishansar Lake, followed by a trek to Gadsar Pass, the highest point of your trek. Continue the journey towards Gadsar Lake, a lake adorned with exotic flowers on both sides. Upon arrival, report to the nearest Army Camp, and after completing the formalities, settle in your camp for an overnight stay.', 'Trek from Vishansar Lake to Gadsar Lake | Walk to the Highest Alpine Lake.', '2025-06-04 09:59:38', '2025-06-04 09:59:38'),
(1834, 5, 44, 'Brace yourself for a thrilling journey through varied terrain, experiencing both flat and challenging inclines as you leave for Satsar Lake. As you ascend, enjoy a brief break at Maengandob, a region surrounded by high mountains. Upon reaching the first of Satsar Lake, get your IDs verified with the army officials and settle yourself in your camps for an overnight stay.', 'Trek from Gadsar Lake to Satsar Lake | Way to the Nest of Seven Small Lakes.', '2025-06-04 09:59:38', '2025-06-04 09:59:38'),
(1835, 6, 44, 'Prepare yourself for an adventurous day as you leave the campsite and ascend to the Gangabal and Nunkol Lakes, passing through the final Satsar Lakes. On the way, admire the views surrounding the trail, along with Gujjar huts and several ridges. As you reach the summit, take-in the views of the twin lakes before continuing your trek toward the sacred lake of the Hindus, Nundkol. Conclude your trek at the beautiful Gangabal Lake, where you will settle at your camps for an overnight stay.', 'Trek from Satsar Lake to Gangabal Twin Lakes | Trail Leading to Foothill of Mt. Haramukh', '2025-06-04 09:59:38', '2025-06-04 09:59:38'),
(1836, 7, 44, 'As you leave the campsite, begin your downhill journey towards Naranag Village, known for its scenic meadows. Upon reaching the village, immerse yourself in the beauty of the place. Also, you can visit the ancient Naranag Temple, dedicated to Lord Shiva. Later, get transferred to the drop-off point in Srinagar, where your trip comes to an end. Have a safe journey back home.', 'Trek from Gangabal Twin Lakes to Naranag | Transfer to Srinagar International Airport.', '2025-06-04 09:59:38', '2025-06-04 09:59:38'),
(1840, 1, 45, 'Pickup From Jammu Tawi Railway Station and Transfer to Katra City. Check Inn to the Hotel Freshen up and relax. Overnight Stay in Hotel at Katra City.', 'Pickup From Jammu Tawi Railway Station and Transfer to Katra City.', '2025-06-04 10:07:01', '2025-06-04 10:07:01'),
(1841, 2, 45, 'Procced For Mata Vaishno Devi Darshan. And Return Back to Katra Hotel. Freshen Up and Relax. Overnight Stay in Hotel at Katra City.', 'Procced For Mata Vaishno Devi Darshan.', '2025-06-04 10:07:01', '2025-06-04 10:07:01'),
(1842, 3, 45, 'Transfer to Jammu Tawi railway Station to connect onward journey with great memories of Joy Tour and Travels.', 'Drop at Jammu Tawi railway Station.', '2025-06-04 10:07:01', '2025-06-04 10:07:01'),
